Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 1984年11月 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:24.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 戈巴契夫上臺前夕 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:27.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 一艘蘇聯颱風級潛艇 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 在大淺灘以南 浮上海面 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:31.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 潛艇後來…下沉深海 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:34.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 顯然是發生了輻射意外 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 部分船員獲救 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 但報導未經證實 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:43.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 蘇美兩國政府作出聲明 )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:47.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 本片所描述的事故… )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 根本從沒發生 )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 波利尼灣 蘇聯潛艇基地以北 )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,( 摩爾曼斯克附近 )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 今早很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's cold this morning, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:48.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:02.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,嚴寒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:02.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's time, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:30.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,的確是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:30.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Time indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:24.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(追擊紅色十月)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你做什麼? 你應該在樓上睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:51.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're supposed to be upstairs sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:57.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 史丹尼不斷吵醒我 - 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:57.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Stanley keeps waking me up. - Oh, I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你越來越重了 - 她最多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You're getting heavy. - No nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,只准喝兩杯水 聽兩個故事 傑克...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:05.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Two stories. Two glasses of water. Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:12.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你快要錯過班機了 - 好吧 聽著 跟韋太太到樓上睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:12.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You're going to miss the plane. - Go upstairs with Mrs. Wheeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這次我會買一個弟弟給史丹尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When I'm on my business trip, I'll get Stanley a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 一言為定? - 一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Promise? - I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:58.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 先生 有什麼吩咐嗎? - 沒有 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:58.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Can I get you anything, sir? - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:03.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,睡一覺吧 時間會過得快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:03.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you try and get some sleep, the flight will go a lot faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:07.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在機上睡不著覺 我怕亂流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:07.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I can never sleep on a plane. Turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼? - 亂流
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Pardon? - Turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:15.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,陽光照射地面 熱空氣上升 冷空氣下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:15.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Solar radiation heats the earth's crust, warm air rises, cool air descends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我不喜歡亂流 - 還是睡一睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I don't like that. - Try to get some sleep anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dr Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:14.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(中央情報局)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,傑克 進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:19.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jack, get yourself in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你看起來很憔悴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus, you look like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:26.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 上將 要咖啡嗎? 我需要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:26.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you very much, Admiral. I could use some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:30.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你一定不享受這次旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:30.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not going to ask you how your flight went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:36.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 上次睡覺是什麼時候? - 我不知道 這表還是倫敦時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:36.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- When did you last get some sleep? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,加糖加奶 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:40.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Milk and sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:46.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,卡露好嗎? 上次在你爺爺家見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:46.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How's Caroline? Last time I saw her was at your granddad's place in Maine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她很好 她問候你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She's fine. She sends you her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:55.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,莎莉呢? 她很好 她有三歲了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:55.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And Sally? What is she now, three?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:59.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,五歲了 人小鬼大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:59.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, she's a very precocious five.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.91,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她說如果我們買一個弟弟 她就不會那麼寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:04.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She announced the other day that her life would be less lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:09.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,買弟弟? 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:09.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,if we were to buy her a baby brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:14.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,後來她叫我們買弟弟給史丹尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:14.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But she decided it would be enough if we were to buy one for Stanley.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:20.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 誰是史丹尼? - 史丹尼是玩具熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:20.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Who's Stanley? - Stanley's a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:27.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼半夜趕乘飛機來這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:27.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's important enough to get you on a plane in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:32.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,英國情報局兩天前 獲得這些照片"赤色十月"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:32.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,British Intelligence obtained these pictures of the Red October.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是最新的颱風級潛艇 真巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She's the latest Typhoon class.  Big son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:40.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,比同類潛艇長十二米 闊三米
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:40.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,12 meters longer than standard. 3 meters wider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長是韋莫斯 - 你曾經調查他?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:44.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain's name is Ramius. - One of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:50.12,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,去年查過他的生平 過去十年 他負責測試各級新潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:50.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I did the bio on him last year. He always takes out their lead boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:55.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,政治關係良好 大部分艦長都是由他一手訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:55.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good political connections. Trains their attack-boat skippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯人叫他"維爾紐斯勒力"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:59.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Russians call him Vilnius nastavnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:03.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"維爾紐斯校長"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Vilnius schoolmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:08.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 這些是什麼門? - 它們正是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:08.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What are these doors? - Those doors are the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:15.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道它是什麼 英國人也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:15.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know what they are, neither do the British. Perhaps they're new.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:19.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我想請一個人看看這些圖片 你認識史泰勒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:19.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'd like to show these to Skip Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 潛艇駕駛員 - 後來遇上車禍 斷了腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:23.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The sub driver? - He was until he lost his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:28.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,現在在軍校教書 當海軍顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:28.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now he teaches at the Academy. He's got top-secret clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪芝 為懷博士準備座駕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Have the car for Dr Ryan downstairs in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:43.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,衛星今早在波利尼灣 發現赤色十月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:43.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The satellite caught Red October in Polijarny Inlet this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:19.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(達拉斯號 洛杉磯級攻擊潛艇)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(波利尼灣西北一百哩)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:29.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 聽到嗎? - 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:29.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do you hear it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:35.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,從前我們會一面睡覺一面監聽 現在聽到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:35.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,At Cal Tech we used to do this in our sleep. Do you hear it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等 這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait a minute... maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 被水面的雜聲蓋過了? - 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's buried in surface clutter. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 用分析儀 - 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I should go to SAPS? - Correct, Seaman Beaumont.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:50.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,採用訊號分析系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:50.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Signal Algorithmic Processing Systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一星期後 你就可以在學院任教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give it a week and you'll be teaching at Cal Tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:59.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,貝多芬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:59.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So, like Beethoven on the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你用電腦創作…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,you have labored to produce...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,生物樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...a biologic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼? - 鯨的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- A what? - A whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:22.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,鯨魚比你更熟悉聲納
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:22.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A marine mammal that knows a lot more about sonar than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:27.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,關閉訊號分析系統 撥去269
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:27.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Kill SAPS. Go over to 269, and let's try it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:33.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,再聽一次 別讓他欺負你 叫他談巴伐洛提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:33.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If he gets to bothering you, ask him about Pavarotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:39.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們沒空聊天 我正在教授水兵寶文…現代聲波定位儀的奧秘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:39.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I was in the middle of teaching Beaumont about modern sonar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:45.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我不是軍士長 我是森林女王 別這樣 - 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:45.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm chief of the boat. - Tell me, Cobb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,水兵鐘斯是超級音樂迷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seaman Jones is into music in a big way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:12:00.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他把這潛艇當作私人音樂廳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:12:00.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He figures this whole boat is his personal, private stereo set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:05.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他拿巴伐洛提的唱片 - 是帕格尼尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:05.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He gets this Pavarotti... - It was Paganini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我在說故事 別歪曲事實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,巴伐洛提是男高音 帕格尼尼是作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:11.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pavarotti is a tenor. Paganini was a composer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:19.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他在潛艇播放唱片 戴上耳筒聽音樂 不亦樂乎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:19.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's got this music, and he's listening to it on his head set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:24.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,後來出事了 聖地牙哥一整隊軍艦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:24.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then all hell breaks loose. There's a slew of boats at San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:30.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 還有珍珠港一艘軍艦 - 他們突然聽到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:30.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- And one way out at Pearl. - All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:35.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,巴伐洛提的歌聲 巴伐洛提… 我們的鐘斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:35.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pavarotti is coming out of their asses. Jones...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我要做什麼? - 由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:40.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What do I do? - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:47.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,指揮台 在097有新發現 指定呼號是S35
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:47.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,New contact bearing 097. Designate contact Sierra-35.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:52.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我是艦長 有什麼發現? 聲音從遠處傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:52.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What have you got, Jonesy?  Probably submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:58.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信是巨獸出籠了 可能是波利尼灣的導彈潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:58.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It could be a missile boat out of Polijarny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:04.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開始追蹤 我馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:04.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Start your track. I'll be there in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:11.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命 是時候啟閱命令了 那位政治委員… 進了艦長室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:11.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Time to open the orders, sir. The Political Officer is in your cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.16,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你守著指揮台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:19.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:44.64,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你做什麼? - 我要監督艦隊成員的穩定性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:44.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What are you doing? - Overseeing the stability of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:49.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你侵犯我的私隱權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:49.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,By invading my privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:55.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,私隱權並不重要 我們是蘇聯子民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:55.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Privacy is not a major concern in the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:59.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,私隱權抵觸國家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:59.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is often contrary to the collective good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:12.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"看 我像賊一樣來臨"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:12.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Behold, I am coming as a thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:18.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"他們聚集在一起 在一個名叫… 哈米吉多頓的地方"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:18.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"And they gathered them together in a place called Armageddon. "
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:25.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"第七位天使把碗倒在空中 天上有一把聲音說…"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:25.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"The 7th angel poured forth his bowl, and a voice cried out from Heaven..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:29.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"成了"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:29.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"It is done."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:34.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你肩負重任 怎能聽信末世預言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:34.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A man with your responsibilities reading about the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:41.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼? "我是摧毀世界的死亡使者"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:41.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's this? "I am become death, the destroyer of worlds."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一位美國人引述這段印度古文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is an ancient Hindu text quoted by an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:48.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 美國人? - 他發明原子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:48.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- An American? - He invented the atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,後來被指為共產黨員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:52.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He was accused of being a communist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:56.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你在這些句子下面劃線、寫字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:56.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You wrote and underlined these passages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:59.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我妻子的遺物 我留作紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:04.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This book belonged to my wife. I keep it for sentimental value.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起…尊夫人是一位美人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry. Your wife was a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她的去世令人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Her death was unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:16.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我只不過在履行職責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:16.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I am only doing my job. It is my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,國安局派了多少特務 來我的船?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:22.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How many KGB agents are aboard my boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:27.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你的船? 是 這潛艇屬於蘇聯人民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:27.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Your boat? This vessel belongs to the people of the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:32.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,假使船上有國安局和情報局的特務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:32.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Besides, if the KGB or the GRU has agents aboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:36.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不會知情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:36.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I would be the last to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:41.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不如啟讀命令吧 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:41.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I suggest we open our orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:45.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好的 同志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:45.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Certainly, comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:31.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,紅旗北軍潛艇部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:31.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,From Commander Strategic Forces Red Banner Northern Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:37.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,戰略指揮部指示…我們向北方座標5490進發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:37.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We are to proceed north, to grid square 5490.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:43.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,和卡華洛夫潛艇會合  艦長是杜普夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:43.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're to rendezvous with Konovalov, Capt. Tupolev's boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:50.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你認識他? - 他是貴族後裔 也是你的門生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You know Tupolev? - I know he was your student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.16,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,據說他特別敬重你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's rumored he has a place in his heart for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:59.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,杜普夫只會敬重自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:59.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's little room in Tupolev's heart for anyone but Tupolev.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:08.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,會合後 兩艘戰艦一起演習 杜普夫追逐我們的戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:08.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We are to make contact and run tests. Tupolev will hunt our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們測試履帶式驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We are to evaluate the readiness of the caterpillar drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:17.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,最後 在本月十六日返回波利尼灣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:17.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We return to Polijarny on or about the 16th of this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:22.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 這是一個歷史時刻 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:22.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is an historic moment. I should like to make a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在提出請求前… 雖然不合常規
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Before you proceed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:29.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但請讓我向船員公佈任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:29.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Would you permit me to post the orders for the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:59.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我要去一個地方 你不能同行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:59.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where I am going, you cannot follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:33.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,柏醫生 立刻來艦長室 這裡發生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:33.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dr Petrov, report to my cabin. There's been a dreadful accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:44.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(美軍船塢 馬里蘭州)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:21.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,下面沒有支船架 快點動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:21.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's no cradle underneath it. Get it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:26.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不要那麼固執 上來幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:26.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to come up here and do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷傑克 誰讓你進來?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ryan! Who let you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:38.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,史泰勒 他們叫你來砌模型?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:38.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Have they got you playing with models now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:44.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,該死的 叫他慢下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:44.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Damn it, Phil! Tell them to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:50.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是模型 這是深潛救助艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:50.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not a model. It's a DSRV. A rescue sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你拿它來做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you doing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:59.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,改裝入塢設計 它可以配合各國潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:59.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're rigging it with a generic docking collar for other subs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在24小時內趕到世界每個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:03.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We can get it anywhere in the world in 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:10.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你的背部沒事吧 - 沒事 有沒有時間?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:10.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How's your back? - It's fine. Have you got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:16.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,比颱風級潛艇更大 這些是什麼門?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:16.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's bigger than a regular Typhoon. What are these doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你真細心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't miss much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它們比魚雷發射管大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Those are too big to be torpedo tubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:28.25,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 用來平射洲際導彈? - 為何要那樣做?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:28.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Can you launch an ICBM horizontally? - Why would you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:33.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它們是對稱的 排在艦軸兩邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:33.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They're symmetrical, right down the long axis of the sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:39.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是聲波定位儀? - 太接近螺旋槳了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:39.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How about a towed sonar array? - Too close to the screws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,怎會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這可能是履帶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:45.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This could be a caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:51.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼? - 履帶式驅動器 磁性壓水式推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:51.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- A what? - Magneto-hydrodynamic propulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 明白嗎? - 不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do you follow? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:58.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它是海底噴射引擎 頭部吸水 尾部噴水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:58.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's like a jet engine for the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:03.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,沒機器要轉動 所以很寧靜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:03.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's got no moving parts, so it's very, very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:08.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 有多靜? - 聲波定位儀也不能發現它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:08.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How quiet? - Sonar wouldn't pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:15.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它的聲音像是鯨魚交配 或是地殼震動 總之不像潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:15.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe as a seismic anomaly. It wouldn't sound like a submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:22.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們數年前 研造這種潛艇 但不成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:22.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We messed with this a few years ago. Couldn't make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:27.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他們成功了? 這不是模型吧 - 它今早出海了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:27.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They really built this? - She put to sea this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:38.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,十二歲時我幫爸爸建造防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:38.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When I was twelve I helped my daddy build a bomb shelter in our basement,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,因為有人打算向佛羅里達州發射飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,because some fool parked a dozen warheads off the coast of Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:49.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這東西能向華盛頓和紐約…發射二百枚飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:49.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This thing could park 200 warheads off Washington or New York
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,而且神不知鬼不覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:55.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and no one would know anything about it until it was all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:08.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 你沒事吧 - 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:08.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you all right, Captain? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:13.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,被地上的茶滑了一跤 竟然斷送生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:13.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's just, to die from something as petty as slipping on tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:17.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別怪責自己 這是意外 回基地後你的心情會平復
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:17.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It was an accident. You'll feel better when we put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:21.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 回基地? - 回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:21.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Put in? - Return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:26.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 船上必須有政治委員 - 醫生 這是蘇聯戰艦 我是指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:26.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We have no political officer. - This is a Soviet combat vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:34.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們不能為這意外撤銷任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:34.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We do not cancel operations because of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:40.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,水兵 過來 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:40.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seaman, come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:45.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 報上名來 - 副廚 羅洛夫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:45.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Your name? - Cook's Assistant Loginov.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 你和醫生來當見證人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you and the doctor to witness this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:56.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我解除政治委員的導彈鑰匙 你們走吧…我來保管鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:56.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm removing the Political Officer's missile key and keeping it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:24:00.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要請示艦隊總司令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:24:00.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We should report this to Red Fleet Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:06.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 我們不能發放無線電
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:06.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's impossible. Our orders are for radio silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:11.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你可以走了 - 艦長 這樣不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:11.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's all, Loginov. - This is most unnerving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:19.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發出兩條鑰匙就是為了避免…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:19.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The reason for having two missile keys is so that no one man may...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:24.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 避免什麼?  - 避免導彈受一人控制
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:24.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- May what? - May arm the missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.84,0:24:29.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 讓我保管鑰匙 - 謝謝 你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.84,0:24:29.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Perhaps I should keep the key. - That'll be all, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:35.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,到時你自會明白 是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.43,0:24:35.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When I address the crew, then you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.44,0:24:45.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,柏道夫 是 我不會向中央報告你的言論
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.44,0:24:45.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Petrov, I will try to forget your comments when I present my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:48.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:48.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.71,0:24:59.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在310的位置 時速十二海裡 離海面二萬碼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.71,0:24:59.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Holding steady on 310. 12 knots at about 20,000 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.71,0:25:04.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 有沒有資料? - 電腦還在分析  雙螺旋槳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.71,0:25:04.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Have you got a make on it? - The computer is chewing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:08.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,聲音像是颱風級潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.93,0:25:08.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It sounds like a Typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.06,0:25:15.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯颱風級潛艇 首次記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:24.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 總部有沒有發放新消息? - 沒有新資料
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:24.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Did I miss something on the boards? - Sub plant hasn't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.99,0:25:31.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 電腦記錄了多少颱風級潛艇? - 六艘
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.99,0:25:31.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How many Typhoons are listed? - Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.54,0:25:37.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,叫它做"颱風七號" 開始監聽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.54,0:25:37.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Call this guy Typhoon 7. Work in a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.25,0:25:45.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 它會聽到我們嗎? - 潛艇有聽覺盲點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.25,0:25:45.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Won't he hear us? - Not if we stay in his baffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.93,0:25:49.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們聽不見螺旋槳背後的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.93,0:25:49.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come in behind his propeller and he's deaf as a post.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:24.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 聲納有新發現嗎? - 沒有 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.33,0:26:24.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Any sonar contacts? - No, the sonar is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.96,0:26:29.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 海面有沒有船隻? - 沒有任何發現
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.96,0:26:29.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do we have any surface contacts? - No, the scope is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:33.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我要向船員說明任務
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.47,0:26:33.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good. Then it's time I explain our orders to the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:38.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,同志們 我是艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:38.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Comrades, this is your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.56,0:26:41.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我感到很榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.56,0:26:41.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is an honor to speak to you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.86,0:26:46.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們駕駛祖國最先進的潛艇 作首次航行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.86,0:26:46.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,while sailing in our motherland's most recent achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.07,0:26:51.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們再次玩危險遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.07,0:26:51.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Once more, we play our dangerous game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:57.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我們的老對手美國海軍 一較高下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.16,0:26:57.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A game of chess, against our old adversary, the American Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.12,0:27:05.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,四十年來 你們的父親和兄長 一直跟他們周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.12,0:27:05.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,For 40 years, your fathers before you, you played this game well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.51,0:27:10.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但現在情況轉變了 我們佔有優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.51,0:27:10.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But today the game is different. We have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:15.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我想起 我們昔日的太空衛星計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:15.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It reminds me of the heady days of Sputnik and Yuri Gagarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.39,0:27:18.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的火箭令世界震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.39,0:27:18.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The world trembled at the sound of our rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.98,0:27:22.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的無聲潛艇 也會令世界震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.98,0:27:22.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It will tremble again at the sound of our silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.65,0:27:26.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,以無聲系統驅動潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.65,0:27:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The order is: Engage the silent drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.90,0:27:30.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開啟外門 是 開啟外門
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.90,0:27:30.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ballast control, open outer doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.91,0:27:34.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,連接履帶式驅動器和主引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.91,0:27:34.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Engage caterpillar and secure main engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.83,0:27:40.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,外門開啟了 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.83,0:27:40.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Doors opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:45.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的艦隊也不知道我們的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.08,0:27:45.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Our own fleet doesn't know our full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.25,0:27:48.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們想測試我們
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.25,0:27:48.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They will test us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:53.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們最終只會自慚形穢 我們要撇下其他艦隻
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:53.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But they will embarrass themselves. We'll leave our fleet behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:58.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,無聲無息地突破美國艦隊的防守
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.51,0:27:58.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We will pass through the American patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.18,0:28:03.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,進入各大城市 一面聽美國搖滾樂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.18,0:28:03.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll lay off their largest city and listen to their rock and roll,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.48,0:28:06.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一面進行導彈演習
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.48,0:28:06.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,while we conduct missile drills.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:13.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們最終只會聽到我們的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:13.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When we are finished, the only sound they will hear is our laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.99,0:28:20.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們笑著去夏灣拿 迎接陽光和熱情的黨員
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.99,0:28:20.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then we will sail to Havana for sunshine and comradeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.75,0:28:28.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 降溫系統已經啟動 - 今天是大日子 我們締造歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.75,0:28:28.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Cryogenic plant coming on line. - A great day. We sail into history.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.05,0:28:38.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,啟動履帶式驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.05,0:28:38.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Caterpillar engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.60,0:28:42.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,履帶式驅動器啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.60,0:28:42.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Caterpillar engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:59.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 發生什麼事? - 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:28:59.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.10,0:29:28.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,左轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.10,0:29:28.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Full rudder left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:32.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,領航員 新航道250
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:32.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Navigator, new course: 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.99,0:29:36.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 新航道250
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.99,0:29:36.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Course: 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.77,0:30:13.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 左舷有聲納接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.77,0:30:13.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sonar contact. Port quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.19,0:30:17.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是美國洛杉磯級潛艇 - 艦長 美國軍艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.19,0:30:17.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- American, Los Angeles class. - American!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.57,0:30:20.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航道310
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.57,0:30:20.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Course: 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.03,0:30:28.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 美軍在跟蹤我們? - 不是 他們保持原來的航道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.03,0:30:28.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Is the American turning to follow us? - No, he is continuing on his course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:32.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 繼續駛向西北方 - 他聽不見我們
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:32.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He is continuing north-west. - He can't hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.05,0:30:36.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,會不會聽見歌聲?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.05,0:30:36.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And the singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.90,0:30:52.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,讓他們唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.90,0:30:52.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let them sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:13.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼? 檢查儀器 正在分析結果 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.96,0:31:13.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you talking about? Check again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.34,0:31:23.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,聲納操作正常 蘇聯人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.34,0:31:23.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The sonar is working. The Russian disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.06,0:31:28.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,本來在艦首四千碼外 然後突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.06,0:31:28.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,One minute he was steady, then he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.69,0:31:34.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我好像聽到… - 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.69,0:31:34.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- And I thought I heard... - Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:39.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我好像聽到歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:39.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I thought I heard singing, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.32,0:31:43.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 歌聲? - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.32,0:31:43.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Singing? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.08,0:31:48.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(莫斯科紅旗艦隊指揮部)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.42,0:31:57.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.42,0:31:57.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.59,0:32:01.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.59,0:32:01.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.51,0:32:06.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.51,0:32:06.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.02,0:32:14.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,早上好 昨晚睡得好嗎 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.02,0:32:14.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good morning, sir. I hope you had a lovely evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:17.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,今早有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A little chilly this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.72,0:32:45.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,馬高韋莫斯寄了一封信來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.72,0:32:45.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's a letter from Marko Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.64,0:32:48.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,馬高
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.64,0:32:48.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Marko!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.25,0:33:21.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.25,0:33:21.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.51,0:33:25.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我是懷博士
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.51,0:33:25.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No, this is Dr Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.01,0:33:31.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 發生什麼事了? - 來 不再是學術研究那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.01,0:33:31.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened? - This is no longer research.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:41.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我找到那些門的資料 你知道它們是什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.40,0:33:41.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I got a line on those doors. You know what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:50.16,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 無聲推進系統 - 你怎麼知道的?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.99,0:33:50.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- A silent propulsion system. - How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.33,0:33:55.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的潛艇曾經發現它 但它消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.33,0:33:55.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The sub captain radioed in. The thing disappeared right in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.58,0:33:58.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這還不止…看 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.58,0:33:58.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's only the half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.22,0:34:11.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 有證件嗎? - 真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.22,0:34:11.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You got your ID? - This is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.85,0:34:16.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,基洛夫級、基輔級、明斯克級
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.85,0:34:16.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Kirov, the Kiev, the Minsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.60,0:34:19.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他們出動了整支艦隊 - 看來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.60,0:34:19.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Their whole fleet. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:27.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我們去哪裡? - 向龐傑飛彙報情況 他是國防顧問
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:27.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where are we going? - Briefing for Jeffrey Pelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.28,0:34:33.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,大部分參謀長都來了 還有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.28,0:34:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The President's Security Advisor. Most of the Joint Chiefs will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.95,0:34:38.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 誰作彙報? - 你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.95,0:34:38.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Who is giving the briefing? - You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.37,0:34:43.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,文書士官準備了幻燈片 你只需…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.37,0:34:43.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All the slides are laid out for you. All you've got to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.68,0:34:51.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有人比你更瞭解這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.68,0:34:51.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, no one understands this material better than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.31,0:34:58.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,向他介紹這潛艇 綜合現有的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.31,0:34:58.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give him a run down of the sub and the stuff in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.44,0:35:02.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他會單刀直入地發問 你實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.44,0:35:02.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When he asks direct questions, give him direct answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.02,0:35:06.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,說明你的想法 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.02,0:35:06.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell him what you think. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.58,0:35:19.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 在過去二十四小時 蘇聯海軍有不尋常舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.58,0:35:19.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The last 24 hours have seen some extraordinary Soviet naval activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.71,0:35:23.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這艘新潛艇被命名為"赤色十月"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.71,0:35:23.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The first ship to sail was the Red October,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:27.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,為了紀念1917年十月革命
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:27.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,in reference to the October revolution of 1917.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.51,0:35:31.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它是颱風級潛艇的變體 有650英尺長
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.51,0:35:31.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A variant of the Typhoon class, she's 650 feet long
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.30,0:35:36.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,排水量是三萬二千噸
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.30,0:35:36.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and 32,000 tons submerged displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.85,0:35:44.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,跟二次大戰的航空母艦相等 艦首和艦尾設有數道門 門後是獨特的推進系統
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.85,0:35:44.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We believe that these doors enclose a unique propulsion system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.15,0:35:48.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,磁性壓水式推進器 又名履帶式驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.15,0:35:48.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A magneto-hydrodynamic drive, or caterpillar,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.82,0:35:52.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,潛艇可以無聲無息地航行
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.82,0:35:52.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,that would enable the sub to run virtually silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.87,0:35:58.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長是最受敬重的指揮官韋莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.87,0:35:58.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is possible that this new drive system allowed Capt. Ramius...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.66,0:36:01.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有他的照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.66,0:36:01.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do we have his picture available?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.83,0:36:07.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他可以避過戰艦的追蹤 達拉斯號今早嘗試跟蹤赤色十月
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.83,0:36:07.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...to elude our attack boat Dallas, which was trailing Red October.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:14.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果這推進器真的能無聲運作
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.80,0:36:14.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is also possible that this drive system
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.39,0:36:19.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,赤色十月可以避過大西洋的警戒網
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.39,0:36:19.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,could render the Red October undetectable to our warning nets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:24.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這潛艇會不會是"先發制人武器"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:24.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Would you characterize this as a first-strike weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:30.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,有此可能
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:30.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That is a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:37.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它可以偷偷接近對手 在毫無先兆的情況下發炮
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:37.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is designed to approach by stealth and armed with nuclear warheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.20,0:36:43.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這船是用來開戰的 說下去 懷先生
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.20,0:36:43.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Damn thing was made to start a war.  Proceed, Mr. Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.71,0:36:47.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,赤色十月突然失蹤 與此同時…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.71,0:36:47.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,After the Dallas lost contact, there were additional sailings.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:53.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,波利尼灣和列寧格勒出動艦隻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:53.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,From Polijarny, Leningrad and from the Mediterranean.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.55,0:36:58.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,駛到波羅的海和地中海 五十八艘核潛艇 正駛向大西洋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.55,0:36:58.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There are now some 58 nuclear subs headed at high speed into the Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.85,0:37:03.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,衛星發現波利尼灣的戰艦在放射熱能
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.85,0:37:03.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This afternoon's satellite pass over Polijarny found heat blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.06,0:37:09.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,超過二十艘巡洋艦和驅逐艦即將出海
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.06,0:37:09.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,indicating that the Kirov, the Minsk and 20 other ships were ready to sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:14.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,郭上將 你有什麼結論
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:14.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This constitutes the bulk of the Soviet surface fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.61,0:37:18.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,現時沒有足夠資料作出結論
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.61,0:37:18.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The data supports no conclusions as yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.12,0:37:27.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,太平洋沒有軍艦 他們可能只是演習 可能… 可能不是演習
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.12,0:37:27.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Absence of activity in the Pacific suggests that this is just an exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:31.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們可能想挑戰北約 國防顧問會談論這一點 法官
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.17,0:37:31.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Suppose this is a move against NATO?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.38,0:37:38.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這是機密消息 絕對不能公開
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.38,0:37:38.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have some very sensitive information. It must not leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:43.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在啟航前 韋莫斯去信給巴度甯上將
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:43.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Before sailing, Ramius sent a letter to Admiral Yuri Padorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.27,0:37:46.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他是紅旗艦隊指揮部的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.27,0:37:46.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's chairman of the Red Fleet Northern Directorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.02,0:37:51.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,韋莫斯的妻子的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.02,0:37:51.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's her uncle, Ramius' wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.61,0:37:54.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她的叔叔 誰的叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.61,0:37:54.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Padorin is her uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.95,0:38:01.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們不知道信件的內容 巴上將立刻和查甯戈總理開會
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.95,0:38:01.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Padorin immediately demanded a meeting with Premier Chenyenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.16,0:38:08.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,數分鐘後 蘇聯海軍追尋赤色十月
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.16,0:38:08.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Within minutes of that meeting, orders were given to find Red October
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.46,0:38:11.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,目的是擊沉它
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.46,0:38:11.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and sink her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.13,0:38:16.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 擊沉它? - 他們要對付瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.13,0:38:16.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sink her? - They've got a madman on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.68,0:38:21.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果它駛入海岸範圍五百哩 我們只有兩分鐘時間作準備
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.68,0:38:21.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Within 500 miles off the coast, we'll have only two minutes' warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:41.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 今天是二十三號? - 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:41.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Today's the 23rd, isn't it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:55.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:55.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.55,0:38:59.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.55,0:38:59.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.10,0:39:06.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你有什麼高見 懷博士?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.10,0:39:06.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you wish to add something to our discussion, Dr Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:16.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可以考慮另一種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.52,0:39:16.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, perhaps there's another possibility we might consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.74,0:39:20.36,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,韋莫斯可能想變節
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.74,0:39:20.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ramius might be trying to defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.53,0:39:23.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你說他想來… - 說下去 懷先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.53,0:39:23.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do you mean to suggest? - Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.16,0:39:32.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,韋莫斯負責訓練軍官
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.16,0:39:32.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ramius trained most of their officer corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:36.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他可以挑選忠於自己的下屬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:36.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He could select men willing to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.96,0:39:40.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他不是俄國人 他生於立陶宛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.96,0:39:40.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's not Russian. He's Lithuanian.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.55,0:39:44.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,由當漁夫的祖父帶大
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.55,0:39:44.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He was raised by his grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.56,0:39:49.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他沒有孩子 沒有家累
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.56,0:39:49.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He has no children. No ties to leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:39:55.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是他妻子首個死忌
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:39:55.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Today is the first anniversary of his wife's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.44,0:40:01.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 別瞎猜 你只是分析員 你怎知道他的心態 - 我認識韋莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.44,0:40:01.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Come on. You're just an analyst. - I know Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:06.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他是潛艇艦隊的傳奇人物 他敢於挑戰政黨
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.74,0:40:06.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's a legend among his men. He's always been a maverick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.58,0:40:11.25,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我在外交宴會見過他 將軍 你認識韋莫斯嗎? 何上將
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.58,0:40:11.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I met him at an embassy dinner. Have you met Capt. Ramius, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.22,0:40:27.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,韋莫斯何時到達導彈發射點?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.22,0:40:27.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How long before Ramius could be in a position to fire his missiles at us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.52,0:40:32.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 四天后 - 我會向總統彙報 現在散會
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.52,0:40:32.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Four days. - All right, I'll brief the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:38.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷博士 請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:38.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dr Ryan, would you stay for a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:42.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫你實話實說 但這次…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:42.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I said speak your mind, Jack, but Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:57.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你令將軍難以下臺
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:57.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You slammed the door on the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.92,0:41:01.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我無意冒犯他 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.92,0:41:01.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That was not my intention. - Yes, it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.63,0:41:07.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他當眾奚落你 你還以顏色 我認為他應有此報
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.63,0:41:07.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He was patronizing you. In my opinion he deserved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.43,0:41:12.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我是政客 政客會說謊使詐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.43,0:41:12.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm a politician, which means I'm a cheat and a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.69,0:41:16.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這一刻在吻嬰孩 轉過臉就搶糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.69,0:41:16.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When I'm not kissing babies, I'm stealing their lollipops.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.40,0:41:21.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但政客會靈活地聽取意見
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.40,0:41:21.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But it also means that I keep my options open.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.57,0:41:27.16,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,現在假設你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.57,0:41:27.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's assume for a minute that you're right,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.33,0:41:33.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這個俄國人想變節 我們該做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.33,0:41:33.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and this Russian intends to defect. What do you suggest we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:39.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 堵截潛艇 -慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:39.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We definitely grab the boat. - Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.09,0:41:43.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他不是米格機機師
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.09,0:41:43.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is not a stray pilot with a MiG.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.51,0:41:48.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他駕駛價值數十億的核潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.51,0:41:48.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're talking about several billion dollars worth of Soviet property.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.64,0:41:53.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 蘇聯會追討這寶物 - 派人登上潛艇調查他們
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.64,0:41:53.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They're going to want it back. - We could inspect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.77,0:41:57.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,編個藉口 進行"海岸例行檢查"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.77,0:41:57.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Call it a Coastguard safety inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.02,0:42:01.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,從何著手?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.02,0:42:01.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.57,0:42:05.36,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,通知大西洋艦隊的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.57,0:42:05.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We need to contact the commanders in the Atlantic directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.53,0:42:10.12,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,千萬不能讓蘇軍窺聽我們的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.53,0:42:10.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If the Russians get one whiff of this, the game is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.28,0:42:13.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,然後我們要制定策略
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.28,0:42:13.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We need to be able to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:18.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備隨時介入 調停這場風波
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:18.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We need to be ready to go at a moment's notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.29,0:42:23.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,最後派人接觸韋莫斯 找出他的動機
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.29,0:42:23.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And somebody has to find out what Ramius' intentions really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.84,0:42:26.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 你何時出發?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.84,0:42:26.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, when do you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.68,0:42:32.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.68,0:42:32.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.18,0:42:36.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,將軍說得對 我只不過是分析員
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.18,0:42:36.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The general was right. I am only an analyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:39.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你是最佳人選 我不能差遣他們
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:39.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're perfect. I can't ask any of these characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.73,0:42:43.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一 他們不信你  二 他們不敢憑直覺行事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.73,0:42:43.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They wouldn't stake their reputations on a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.48,0:42:46.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 而你… - 可以被犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.48,0:42:46.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You... - Are expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.74,0:42:51.91,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.74,0:42:51.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.16,0:42:57.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在三天之內證實你的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.16,0:42:57.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll give you three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.79,0:43:04.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,否則我們要消滅韋莫斯 你接受任務嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.79,0:43:04.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,After that, I have to hunt down Ramius and destroy him. Will you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.19,0:43:23.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.19,0:43:23.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mother of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.48,0:43:29.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,立刻下潛至九百米 發生什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.48,0:43:29.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Secure the masts. All ahead two thirds. Set depth to 900 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.53,0:43:37.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,左轉至205 205航線確定
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.53,0:43:37.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come left, heading 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.43,0:43:58.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,命令是七小時前頒佈的 到底是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.43,0:43:58.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,These orders are seven bloody hours old!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.35,0:44:01.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 - 全速前進…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.35,0:44:01.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain? - All ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.15,0:44:07.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,問工程師反應器可否推動至百分之一百零五
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.15,0:44:07.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Inquire of the engineer about going to 105% on the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.49,0:44:13.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,七小時了 整支艦隊在追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.49,0:44:13.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seven hours! The entire fleet is after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.17,0:44:23.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,到達九百米 好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.17,0:44:23.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,900 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.04,0:44:30.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 反應器可推動至百分之一百零五 但這不是好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.04,0:44:30.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,105% on the reactor is possible... but not recommended.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.27,0:44:44.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,把反應器推動至百分之一百零五
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.27,0:44:44.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Go to 105 on the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.73,0:44:52.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 什麼事? 我們去哪裡? - 去殺一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.73,0:44:52.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What is it? Where are we going? - We're going to kill a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.70,0:44:57.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們去殺韋莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.70,0:44:57.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're going to kill Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.35,0:45:21.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,從沒喝過這麼難喝的羅宋湯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.35,0:45:21.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you like borscht perhaps, but I've eaten better in the galley.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.10,0:45:27.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我太太對待應說… 這廚子在阿富汗學烹飪?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.10,0:45:27.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My wife asked the waiter if the chef was from Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.57,0:45:31.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,然後我們去看芭蕾舞 那位新舞蹈員真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.57,0:45:31.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then we went on to the ballet, to see the new girl as Giselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.15,0:45:36.66,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她嫁給工廠經理
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.15,0:45:36.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Remember how beautiful she was? She just married a factory manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.82,0:45:43.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾了 醫生 有沒有最新的輻射測驗資料
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.82,0:45:43.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Doctor, do you have the figures for the last batch of radiation tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.58,0:45:45.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,現在要?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.58,0:45:45.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.13,0:45:49.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.13,0:45:49.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.46,0:45:55.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,上一次測驗的資料 也拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.46,0:45:55.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bring the preceding set as well, for comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.43,0:45:58.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.43,0:45:58.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.99,0:46:18.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他不會這麼快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.99,0:46:18.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It will take him some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.49,0:46:24.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在開始前 我想瞭解布田的死因
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.49,0:46:24.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Before we begin, I'd like to know what happened to Putin.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.25,0:46:36.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他不是真的滑倒吧 - 我不喜歡你的語氣 史勒雲
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.25,0:46:36.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He didn't slip on his tea, did he? - I don't think I like your tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.72,0:46:43.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼語氣有何相干? 我們身犯險境 - 布田會帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.72,0:46:43.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're risking our lives here. - Putin could have made complications.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.10,0:46:48.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你以為他會袖手旁觀 成全我們?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.10,0:46:48.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you think he would go away and sulk?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.31,0:46:54.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他被謀殺? 我的天 - 別呼天喊地
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.31,0:46:54.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you saying he was murdered? - Stop whining, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:58.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我不覺得可惜 他是混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:58.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So he was murdered. The man was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.12,0:47:03.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但我們應該一起做決定
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.12,0:47:03.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But it is a decision we should have all made together.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.45,0:47:08.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是指揮官 如果真相敗露 船員會叛變
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.45,0:47:08.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If the crew finds out, we could have a mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.67,0:47:14.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,船上每一件事都會影響我們
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.67,0:47:14.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Everything that happens on this ship affects us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.84,0:47:20.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 現在還可以回去… - 不能回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.84,0:47:20.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Why don't we go back? - There'll be no going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.64,0:47:26.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,啟航前 我寄信給巴度甯上將
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.64,0:47:26.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Before we sailed I dispatched a letter to Admiral Padorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.64,0:47:31.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我在信內 宣佈了變節計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.64,0:47:31.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,in which I announced our intention to defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.77,0:47:36.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.77,0:47:36.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In the name of God, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.36,0:47:41.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,到達新世界後 科爾特燒掉所有船
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.36,0:47:41.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When he reached the new world, Cortez burned his ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.20,0:47:46.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 手下只好跟他一起奮鬥 - 你把我們置之死地
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.20,0:47:46.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Thus, his men were well motivated. - You have signed our death warrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.87,0:47:52.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 上將會派整支艦隊來 - 他們會找尋、追捕我們
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.87,0:47:52.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Padorin will send the entire fleet. - Jesus! They'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.71,0:47:57.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有人會來找我們 住口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.71,0:47:57.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody is going to find us. That's enough, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.55,0:48:03.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你一定要通知他? 把潛艇交給美國是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.55,0:48:03.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You couldn't just turn the sub over to the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.22,0:48:06.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你還要發表政治宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.22,0:48:06.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You had to make a political statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.14,0:48:13.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,背後隱藏著什麼心態? 為何不能靜靜地溜走?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.14,0:48:13.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Or was it something deeper that made you unable to simply slip away?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.02,0:48:20.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是虛榮心作崇吧 我們為著不同的原因變節
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.02,0:48:20.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Was it ego, Captain? We each have our reasons, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.70,0:48:25.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,收到這潛艇的藍圖後 我開始思變
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.70,0:48:25.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My own began the day I was handed the blueprints for this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.49,0:48:30.12,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這潛艇本來只有一個用途
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.49,0:48:30.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A ship which had but one use. As for the rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:34.84,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我改變它的用途 我會負上全責
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:34.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,those are things that I alone must carry the burden for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:41.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,安東尼 你害怕我們的艦隊? 你應該害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.05,0:48:41.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Anatoly, you're afraid of our fleet. You should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.80,0:48:46.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信 我們有三分一的勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.80,0:48:46.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Personally, I give us... one chance in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.31,0:48:54.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,要茶嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.31,0:48:54.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,More tea, anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.57,0:48:58.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不要了?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.57,0:48:58.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.57,0:49:01.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你們可以回崗位了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.57,0:49:01.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Then you may report back to your posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:21.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,聽到艦長的命令吧 散會
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.13,0:49:21.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You heard the captain, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.56,0:49:31.64,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.56,0:49:31.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.70,0:49:49.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會在他們面前反駁你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.70,0:49:49.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I would never disagree with you in front of the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.54,0:49:53.25,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但這次偉圖說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.54,0:49:53.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But in this case Victor was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:58.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不通知莫斯科會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.41,0:49:58.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It would have been better if you had not informed Moscow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.54,0:50:04.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,莫斯科不足為患 蘇聯海軍也不難對付
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.54,0:50:04.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Moscow is not the worry, nor the whole Soviet Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:09.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我瞭解他們的戰略 我有優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.30,0:50:09.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I know their tactics. I have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.64,0:50:16.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,美國人才教人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.64,0:50:16.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The worry is the Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.69,0:50:21.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,遇上適當的對手才會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.69,0:50:21.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If we meet the right sort, this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.07,0:50:28.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果對方性急魯莽…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.07,0:50:28.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If we get some buckaroo...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:37.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,有亂流…你不喜歡坐飛機?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.66,0:50:37.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Some turbulence. You don't like flying?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.63,0:50:41.84,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這不算是什麼 數月前的亂流才厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.63,0:50:41.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is nothing. You should have been here five months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.00,0:50:46.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,嘔吐更是不在話下 我們在日本海遇上雹暴
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.00,0:50:46.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Talk about puke! We ran into a hail storm over the Sea of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.88,0:50:51.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,每個人都吐得死去活來 機師吐在擋風玻璃上
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.88,0:50:51.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The pilot shot his lunch all over the windshield.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.60,0:50:54.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我往無線電吐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.60,0:50:54.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I barfed on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.43,0:51:00.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一切傾囊而出 分量驚人 那是重量級嘔吐
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.43,0:51:00.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It wasn't that lightweight stuff. It was that chunky industrial puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.57,0:51:03.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要吃一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.57,0:51:03.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:07.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,下次把你的高見 寫下來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.15,0:51:07.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Next time I get a bright idea, I'll put it in a memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.83,0:51:21.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 長官 - 你可以走了 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.83,0:51:21.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sir. - That will be all, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.67,0:51:26.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 偉密斯那班機怎麼了?  - 他們遇上強風
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.67,0:51:26.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Did that Hawkeye trap? - Number four wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.80,0:51:31.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 那還不算太差 - 這位先生想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.80,0:51:31.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Not bad considering. - The gentleman is here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:34.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,先生? 你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.18,0:51:34.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.43,0:51:39.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 郭上將說 穿軍服才不會惹人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.43,0:51:39.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I apologize for the uniform. It's Admiral Greer's idea of a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.48,0:51:45.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你是郭上將的下屬 是的 告訴我 到底發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.48,0:51:45.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you're working for Jim Greer, you can tell me what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.82,0:51:53.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 你有時間嗎?  鐘斯發現了一些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.82,0:51:53.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain, have you got a minute? Here's something you ought to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.04,0:52:00.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你去喝點咖啡 叫他們送茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.04,0:52:00.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get yourself a cup of coffee. I'll have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.46,0:52:03.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長要一杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.46,0:52:03.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get the captain a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.51,0:52:13.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,颱風七號消失後 我聽到歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.51,0:52:13.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The moment that sub went silent and I thought I heard singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.26,0:52:20.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,然後 我聽到一些微弱的聲音 等其他潛艇離去後 我錄下這些音調
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.26,0:52:20.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I heard something in the background, too, and I managed to get it on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.19,0:52:25.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我用電腦過濾聲帶 剩下這聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.19,0:52:25.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I washed it through the computer and managed to isolate this sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.28,0:52:33.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,電腦認為 這是"岩漿移位"的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.28,0:52:33.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The computer identified it as magma displacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.49,0:52:38.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這套軟體 本來是用來探測地震
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.49,0:52:38.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The SAPS software was originally written to look for seismic events.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.70,0:52:42.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 它用地震來解釋陌生的音調
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.70,0:52:42.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,When it gets confused, it runs home to momma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.71,0:52:45.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我不知道你想說什麼 - 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.71,0:52:45.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm not following you. - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.88,0:52:48.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,請聽一聽 把聲帶加速十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.88,0:52:48.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen to it at ten times speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.47,0:53:00.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這一定是人為的聲音 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.47,0:53:00.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's got to be man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.98,0:53:07.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,首次接觸是9時15分 位置是269
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.98,0:53:07.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The first contact was at 09:15 and the bearing was 269.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.48,0:53:12.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,9時30分的時候它在這裡 我在11時和11時15分再發現它
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.48,0:53:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,At 09:30, it was here. At 11 and 11:15, it was here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.99,0:53:18.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯潛艇可以高速駛過雷克雅海脊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.99,0:53:18.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Russian subs have been reported running Reykjanes Ridge at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.87,0:53:22.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 因為他們掌握了海底懸崖的地勢 - 他們有"紅航線一號"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.87,0:53:22.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They had hyper-accurate maps. - Yeah, Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:27.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,海底懸崖的入口是托爾雙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:27.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The front door to those canyons was a location called Thor's Twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.50,0:53:29.84,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.50,0:53:29.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.77,0:53:47.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,直驅"紅航線一號" 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.77,0:53:47.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right into Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.65,0:53:55.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我可能瘋了 但我相信這是蘇聯潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.65,0:53:55.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You may think I'm crazy, but I'll bet we found some new Russian sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.24,0:53:59.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它駛向冰島海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.24,0:53:59.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's now headed for the Iceland coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.49,0:54:06.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我有沒有聽錯了? 你不信任價值四千萬的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.49,0:54:06.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A $40 million computer tells you you're chasing an earthquake,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.21,0:54:11.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你要另找答案?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.21,0:54:11.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,but you don't believe it. And you come up with this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.71,0:54:17.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是的  別緊張 我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.71,0:54:17.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, sir. Relax, you've sold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.89,0:54:25.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,湯姆 你計畫路線 趕去"紅航線一號"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.89,0:54:25.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Plot us a course for the bottom end of Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.77,0:54:31.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,進了海底懸崖就無法找到他們 上升至潛望鏡深度 我們要通知總部
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.77,0:54:31.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll never find him in those canyons. But first we'd better phone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.44,0:54:34.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.44,0:54:34.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.33,0:54:44.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.33,0:54:44.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hang on, Jonesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.88,0:54:52.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我們走近它 你可以追蹤它嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.88,0:54:52.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If I can get you close enough, can you track this sucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.13,0:54:59.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我聽過它的聲音 它逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.13,0:54:59.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Now that I know what to listen for... I'll bag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.72,0:55:04.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 繼續工作 - 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.72,0:55:04.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Carry on. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.48,0:55:11.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,真是荒天下之大謬
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.48,0:55:11.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the craziest notion ever! An entire nuclear submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.27,0:55:15.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,指軍官和導彈潛艇? 全體成員都想變節?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.27,0:55:15.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They can't all want to defect, even if it's only the officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.78,0:55:19.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他有什麼計畫? - 計畫?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.78,0:55:19.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's his plan? - His plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.49,0:55:22.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯人連上廁所 也會預先計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.49,0:55:22.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Russians don't take a dump without a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.12,0:55:27.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,高級軍官不會貿然冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.12,0:55:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Senior captains are sure to have thought the matter through.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.96,0:55:32.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他去紐約宣佈"我來了"? - 可能只是這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.96,0:55:32.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's just going to sail into New York? - It might be that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.46,0:55:35.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在中情局紙上談兵當然簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.46,0:55:35.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Things might be simple at CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.51,0:55:40.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在北大西洋面對整隊蘇聯戰艦 那就比較複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.51,0:55:40.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But in the middle of the North Atlantic they get a bit more complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.89,0:55:44.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 抽煙嗎? - 不 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.89,0:55:44.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Smoke? - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.68,0:55:49.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"海岸例行檢查"是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.68,0:55:49.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And you'd need more than a few days' inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.19,0:55:53.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,單是研究金屬就要花幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.19,0:55:53.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In order to be any value, you'd have to tear it apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.78,0:55:59.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 那我們就扣押潛艇 - 怎樣處置那群船員?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.78,0:55:59.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Then we have to keep it. - What will you do with the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.24,0:56:02.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不願變節的人會回去告發我們
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.24,0:56:02.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They'd know we got the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.16,0:56:09.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你打算殺了他們? - 我們不是在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.16,0:56:09.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Or do you plan to eliminate them? - We're not at war, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.37,0:56:15.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要令他們離開潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.37,0:56:15.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So we have to do this in such a way that they think we don't have the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.25,0:56:19.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不能讓蘇聯知道…我們得到潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.25,0:56:19.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They'll go back and report that we don't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.26,0:56:24.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,否則說什麼也沒用 對嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.26,0:56:24.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Otherwise this whole business is just academic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.60,0:56:26.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.60,0:56:26.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, I see your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.64,0:56:34.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你上次睡覺是什麼時候? - 那是很久之前了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.64,0:56:34.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- When was the last time you slept? - A while.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.82,0:56:39.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 外面的長官會打點一切 - 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.82,0:56:39.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The chief outside will fix you up. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.11,0:56:42.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.11,0:56:42.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.54,0:56:50.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,天快亮了 我們在戰鬥情報中心
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.54,0:56:50.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It'll be dawn soon. We'll be in the CIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.21,0:56:55.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要面對種種危機 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.21,0:56:55.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Things are liable to get a little dicey around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.55,0:57:07.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你認為他瘋了? - 瘋得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.55,0:57:07.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You think he's crazy? - Certifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.97,0:57:12.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想見到他穿軍服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.97,0:57:12.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I don't care for him wearing the uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.35,0:57:18.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,看到那戒指嗎? 72年畢業 他是海軍陸戰隊成員
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.35,0:57:18.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you see that ring on his finger? The Academy class of '72. A Marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.32,0:57:25.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎知道… 是郭告訴我的 三年級時 他在直升機上遇上意外
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.32,0:57:25.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In the summer of his third year, he went down in a chopper accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.37,0:57:32.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他花了十個月 接受牽引治療 花一年學走路
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.37,0:57:32.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He spent ten months in traction and another year learning to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.58,0:57:37.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,第四年 是在醫院念的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.58,0:57:37.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He did his fourth year from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.59,0:57:43.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以考慮給他一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.59,0:57:43.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's up to you, Charlie, but you might consider cutting him a little slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.14,0:57:49.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,反正蘇聯人會先找到那潛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.14,0:57:49.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Russians will find that sub before we get near it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.62,0:58:15.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 正在穿越托爾雙峰 - 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.62,0:58:15.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Passing Thor's Twins, sir. - Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:23.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 穿越托爾雙峰 - 好 開始進入航道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:23.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Passing the Twins now, sir. - Commence your run.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.84,0:58:27.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,拐彎時通知我 是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.84,0:58:27.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Call me when you get to the first turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.22,0:58:31.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,卡馬夫 開始進入航道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.22,0:58:31.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mr. Kamarov, commence your run.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.43,0:58:37.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 開始第一階段 航線260 時速18海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.43,0:58:37.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,First leg on my mark. Course: 260. Speed: 18 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.94,0:58:40.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,深潛270米
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.94,0:58:40.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Depth: 270 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.86,0:58:46.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,五、四、三、二、一
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.86,0:58:46.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.24,0:58:48.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.24,0:58:48.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.70,0:58:54.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航線260 是 航線260 時速18海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.70,0:58:54.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Diving Command, course: 260. Speed: 18 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.66,0:59:01.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別慌張 給我碼錶和地圖 我能駕駛沒有窗的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.66,0:59:01.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give me a stopwatch and a map and I'll fly the Alps in a plane with no windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.59,0:59:05.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但地圖一定要準確
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.59,0:59:05.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If the map is accurate enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.19,0:59:29.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們進了航道 接近首個彎口
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.19,0:59:29.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're in the lane and approaching the first turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.45,0:59:34.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,三十秒後左轉到195
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.45,0:59:34.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come left to course 195 in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.54,0:59:39.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,上升200米 保持速度
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.54,0:59:39.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Decrease depth to 200 meters. Maintain speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.67,0:59:45.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 接近首個彎口25秒後 轉到195
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.67,0:59:45.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain, we are approaching the first turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.92,0:59:50.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,加速至26海裡 重新計算
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.92,0:59:50.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Increase speed to 26 knots and recompute.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.89,0:59:55.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.89,0:59:55.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.98,0:59:59.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,加速至26海裡 重新計算
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.98,0:59:59.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Navigator, recompute for 26 knots.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:05.36,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備拐彎 五、四、三
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:05.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn on my mark. Five, four, three...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.53,1:00:08.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,二、一 開始
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.53,1:00:08.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...two, one, mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.57,1:00:13.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,左轉到195 提升艦首
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.57,1:00:13.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Diving control, come left to 195. Up on the bow planes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.29,1:00:26.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航線195 保持時速26海裡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.29,1:00:26.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Course now 195 and maintaining speed 26 knots.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.09,1:00:35.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 卡馬夫先生 - 下一階段
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.09,1:00:35.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Mr. Kamarov? - Next leg, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.35,1:00:41.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,右轉到240 八分四十秒後拐彎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.35,1:00:41.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come right to 240 at 8 minutes and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.19,1:00:44.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,很好 保持航道和速度
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.19,1:00:44.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very good. Maintain course and speed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.90,1:00:51.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,太快了…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.90,1:00:51.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Too fast, Vassily.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.66,1:00:57.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,該用什麼速度 圖表寫得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.66,1:00:57.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Those charts are laid out precisely. So many knots for so many seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.25,1:01:02.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 這艘船會捱不住的 - 小心說話 史勒雲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.25,1:01:02.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- This thing handles like a pig. - Watch your bearing, Mr. Slavin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.34,1:01:12.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,十五秒後轉彎 要減速嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.34,1:01:12.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,15 seconds to turn. Should we decrease speed?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.43,1:01:16.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不 準備右轉 遵命
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.43,1:01:16.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Negative. Prepare to come right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.68,1:01:21.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,八、七、六、五、四...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.68,1:01:21.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Eight, seven, six, five, four...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.56,1:01:25.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,...三、二、一 開始
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.56,1:01:25.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...three, two, one, mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.48,1:01:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦首俯傾15度 右轉到240 快點
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.48,1:01:31.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,15 degrees on the bow planes. Come right. 240. Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.63,1:01:55.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們位置正確 下一階段 34分鐘後 抵達海王山丘
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.63,1:01:55.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're in the lane. Next leg 34 minutes to the Neptune Massif.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.85,1:01:58.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航道240
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.85,1:01:58.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Course: 240.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.03,1:02:14.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 發生什麼事? - 降溫系統故障 磁石無法降溫
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.03,1:02:14.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened? - The cryogenic plant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.91,1:02:20.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,履帶溫度高出了五十度 還在不斷上升
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.91,1:02:20.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The magnets aren't being cooled. We're 50 degrees above red line.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.20,1:02:25.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 如果不關掉它 它會熔化 - 關掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.20,1:02:25.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's going to melt. - Kill it, shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.71,1:02:35.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 降溫系統失靈了 - 反應器有否損毀
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.71,1:02:35.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The cryogenic plant failed. - Reactor damage?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.38,1:02:39.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 能源輸送失靈 - 反應器自動關閉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.38,1:02:39.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The reactor scrammed automatically. - Was there any core damage?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.14,1:02:43.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 核心有否損壞? 有否洩漏輻射? - 尚未知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.14,1:02:43.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Any radiation leakage? - I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.68,1:02:49.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 要花多少時間修理? - 先要找出原因 可能是液態氦出事 或者是超導體故障
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.68,1:02:49.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How long will it take to fix? - I've got to find out what's wrong first.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.53,1:02:55.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要停下來 修理履帶系統
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.53,1:02:55.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We will have to stop and repair the caterpillar unit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.61,1:03:01.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 不行 以普通推進系統航行 - 艦長 船會發出聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.61,1:03:01.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We will run on normal propulsion. - Captain, we will not be silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.12,1:03:07.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,時速改為20海裡 開動螺旋槳
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.12,1:03:07.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Make revolutions for 20 knots and engage the propellers.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.42,1:03:16.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是 艦長 - 他會把我們害死
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.42,1:03:16.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Aye, Captain. - That man will get us all killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.14,1:03:24.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長自有分寸
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.14,1:03:24.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The captain knows what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.02,1:03:32.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,海軍行動? 我不瞭解這些事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.02,1:03:32.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Naval activities? I have no knowledge of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.57,1:03:36.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我沒當過海員 - 領使先生
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.57,1:03:36.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- But then I never was a sailor. - Mr. Ambassador...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.86,1:03:41.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,貴國在北大西洋 有一百艘軍艦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.86,1:03:41.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You have nearly 100 naval vessels operating in the North Atlantic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.91,1:03:45.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,貴國的戰機 拋下無數聲納浮標
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.91,1:03:45.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You've dropped enough sonar buoys
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.25,1:03:50.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以踏著浮標 由格陵蘭走到蘇格蘭
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.25,1:03:50.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,for a man to walk from Greenland to Scotland without getting his feet wet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.75,1:03:55.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你表達得很清楚海面的情況…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.75,1:03:55.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You make your point as delicately as ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.05,1:04:00.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,軍事演習可能是戰爭的前奏
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.05,1:04:00.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What looks like an exercise could be a prelude to war.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.10,1:04:06.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎能分辨虛實? 我們必須派船去監視你們
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.10,1:04:06.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How can we tell the difference? We have to deploy our ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.31,1:04:09.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你的政府可能會起了戒心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.31,1:04:09.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Has your government considered
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.48,1:04:15.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,雙方的船艦和戰機太過接近
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.48,1:04:15.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,that having your ships and ours in such proximity
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.44,1:04:21.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這種情況會引起戰爭
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.44,1:04:21.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,is inherently dangerous? Wars have begun that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.04,1:04:35.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我們遺失了一艘潛艇 - 遺失?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.04,1:04:35.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We have lost one of our submarines. - Lost it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.88,1:04:38.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它可能沉沒了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.88,1:04:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is most embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.13,1:04:45.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,說出來真尷尬 船上的軍官…他們是高幹子弟
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.13,1:04:45.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Several of the crew, the officers, are sons of high Party officials.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.85,1:04:51.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,其中一位是中央委員的兒子 名字不便透露
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.85,1:04:51.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,One is even the son of a Central Committee member.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.90,1:04:57.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你們正在進行拯救行動? - 對
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.90,1:04:57.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- This is a massive rescue operation? - That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.03,1:05:04.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,真遺憾 我們可怎樣幫忙?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.03,1:05:04.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm terribly sorry. How can we help?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.95,1:05:11.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 看來… - 進行聯合拯救?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.95,1:05:11.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm not sure that... - Perhaps a joint rescue mission?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.88,1:05:17.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.88,1:05:17.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That is very gracious of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.09,1:05:21.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我會傳達你的好意
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.09,1:05:21.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I will pass your offer on.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.22,1:05:24.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,暫時我們不需要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.22,1:05:24.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I think we're doing everything that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.65,1:05:33.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(熊狐步號 蘇聯反核潛艇戰機)
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.02,1:05:34.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(冰島以南)
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.24,1:05:46.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.24,1:05:46.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.74,1:05:54.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們根據你的答案 制定戰略 艦隊會找到我們…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.74,1:05:54.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Our strategy depends on your answer. The fleet will know where we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.79,1:05:59.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 聲納有發現 渦輪螺旋槳式飛機在上空盤旋
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.79,1:05:59.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sonar. We have just been overflown by a low-altitude, multi-engined plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.88,1:06:02.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開動傳聲器
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.88,1:06:02.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Put it on audio.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.09,1:06:10.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,收到短音波 水面有小物件
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.09,1:06:10.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's closing. Water entry of small objects.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.56,1:06:14.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是聲納浮標 - 準備作戰…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.56,1:06:14.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sonar buoys. - Battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.81,1:06:17.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.81,1:06:17.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.07,1:06:21.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,要花多久才到達海王山丘?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.07,1:06:21.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How long to Neptune Massif?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.86,1:06:26.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 多久?  - 四分零十秒
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.86,1:06:26.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How long? - 4 minutes, 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.66,1:06:30.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 要下潛嗎? - 太遲了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.66,1:06:30.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Should we bottom the boat? - It's too late for that now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.87,1:06:36.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不 時間不夠 準備發射導彈 遵命
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.87,1:06:36.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're out of time. Counter measures. Prepare to launch a full spread.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.13,1:06:48.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,請核准發射武器
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.13,1:06:48.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Request permission to launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:51.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可以發射武器
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:51.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Launch the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.52,1:06:55.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,武器發射了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.52,1:06:55.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Weapon is away.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.48,1:07:04.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,高速螺旋 水裡有魚雷
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.48,1:07:04.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,High-speed screw. Torpedo in the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.74,1:07:09.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷發射了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.74,1:07:09.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo is active.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.49,1:07:13.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是實彈魚雷 - 魚雷已經鎖定目標
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.49,1:07:13.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Torpedo has acquired. - Launch counter measures.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.58,1:07:16.25,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航道位置正確
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.58,1:07:16.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.50,1:07:26.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 何時到達海王山丘 - 兩分零九秒後
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.50,1:07:26.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How long to the turn? - 2 minutes, 9 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.72,1:07:30.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,進了深谷就無法逃生 如果反魚雷…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.72,1:07:30.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We've no room to maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.22,1:07:32.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.22,1:07:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.60,1:07:42.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷接近反魚雷 魚雷失去蹤影
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.60,1:07:42.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo has reached counter measures and lost contact.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.24,1:07:51.16,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷再次鎖定目標 魚雷再次追著我們
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.24,1:07:51.16,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo has reacquired and is homing.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.33,1:07:56.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 報告形勢 - 在山丘拐彎 30秒後右轉40度
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.33,1:07:56.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Give me the count. - Turn at Massif in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.96,1:08:00.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 魚雷命中目標的時間 - 三十五秒後命中目標
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.96,1:08:00.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Time to torpedo impact? - 35 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.88,1:08:04.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 加速前進 - 加速前進
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.88,1:08:04.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Increase to flank. - Full-ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.09,1:08:11.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷四十秒後 命中目標 三十五秒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.09,1:08:11.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo impact now 40 seconds. 35 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.06,1:08:21.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,三十秒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.06,1:08:21.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.02,1:08:26.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,接近山丘彎角 七、六…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.02,1:08:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn at Massif in seven, six...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.36,1:08:29.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,...五 四...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.36,1:08:29.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...five, four...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.78,1:08:33.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,...三 二 一 開始
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.78,1:08:33.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...three, two, one, mark.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.04,1:08:38.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 魚雷二十五秒後 命中目標 - 要拐彎了 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.04,1:08:38.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Torpedo impact: 25 seconds. - The turn, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.38,1:08:45.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,等一會 延遲了八秒 九秒 十秒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.38,1:08:45.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mark plus eight seconds, nine, ten...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.84,1:08:52.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,...十一秒 十二秒、十三秒 十四秒、十五秒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.84,1:08:52.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...11 seconds, 12, 13, 14... plus 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.97,1:08:58.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 我們離開了正確位置 - 魚雷在十五秒後 命中目標
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.97,1:08:58.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain, we're out of position. - Torpedo impact in 15 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.64,1:09:01.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發出警告
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.64,1:09:01.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sound collision.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.06,1:09:06.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 我們離開了航道 - 你退下崗位
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.06,1:09:06.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're out of the lane. - You're relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.28,1:09:17.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,右轉 右轉 調整右軸
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.28,1:09:17.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right full rudder! Reverse starboard engine!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.75,1:09:24.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷十二秒後命中目標
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.75,1:09:24.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo impact: 12 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.09,1:09:31.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,十、九、八、七、六、五…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.09,1:09:31.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,10, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.55,1:09:39.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,領航員 報告度數 偏離了十六度
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.55,1:09:39.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Navigator, 16 degrees off the bow plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.29,1:10:07.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他們向我們發炮 - 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.29,1:10:07.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They're really shooting at us! Why? - Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.96,1:10:12.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果他們真的發炮 我們早已死了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.96,1:10:12.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If they were really shooting at us, we'd be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.37,1:10:36.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道履帶出了什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.37,1:10:36.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I found out what happened to the caterpillar.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.83,1:10:43.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,緩衝器被破壞 履帶遲早會負荷過重
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.83,1:10:43.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The buffer circuit has been torn out. It was only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.42,1:10:50.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你說什麼? - 有人暗地裡破壞履帶
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.42,1:10:50.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What are you saying? - Somebody wanted to cripple the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.55,1:10:53.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 艦上有內奸
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.55,1:10:53.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We have a saboteur on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.98,1:11:05.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,軍官不會等到啟航後才動手 這一定是水兵做的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.98,1:11:05.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It can't be any of the officers, it must be a member of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.99,1:11:11.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,翻查布田的檔案 調查海員身分
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.99,1:11:11.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Go and check Putin's files for information on the crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.20,1:11:13.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可能要提早遣散水兵
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.20,1:11:13.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We may have to put them off before we planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.12,1:11:20.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯人連上廁所 也會預先計畫
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.12,1:11:20.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Your average Russkie don't take a dump without a plan."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.54,1:11:25.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,慢著
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.54,1:11:25.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.46,1:11:30.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們不必想辦法叫船員離開潛艇 他自然會趕走他們
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.46,1:11:30.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He will already have figured out how to get the crew off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.76,1:11:38.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們只需猜想他的計畫
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.76,1:11:38.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We just have to figure out how he's going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.85,1:11:42.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他會怎樣趕走船員?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.85,1:11:42.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They'd have to want to get off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.19,1:11:49.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,船員要有離艇的意圖 船員為什麼想離開潛艇?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.19,1:11:49.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do you get a crew to want to get off a submarine?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.20,1:11:53.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,船員為什麼想離開核潛…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.20,1:11:53.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do you get a crew to want to get off a nuclear?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.45,1:11:57.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我知道他會怎樣趕走船員 - 我很忙
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.45,1:11:57.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I know how he'll get the crew off. - Not now, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.66,1:12:04.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,揚基一號 報告情況
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.66,1:12:04.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yankee One, declaring an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.50,1:12:10.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,揚基一號要求導航 位置是270
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.50,1:12:10.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yankee One, vector 270. Speed is buster, over.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.51,1:12:12.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,揚基一號 再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.51,1:12:12.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Say again, Yankee One.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.14,1:12:18.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,熊狐步號太接近部隊 它和一架F14戰機相撞
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.14,1:12:18.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A Bear Foxtrot got too close to the group. He bumped one of our F-14s.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.73,1:12:24.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,戰機水壓下降 他們引導它返回母艦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.73,1:12:24.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The plane's damaged. They're trying to get him back aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.36,1:12:27.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,真忙碌
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.36,1:12:27.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Busy morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.32,1:12:32.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚蘇聯戰艦在東邊港口戒備
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.32,1:12:32.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Russian attack subs have taken up station off every East Coast port.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.03,1:12:35.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.03,1:12:35.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.70,1:12:38.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,新澤西艦隊趕到海岸
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.70,1:12:38.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The New Jersey and her group are moving up the coast.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.12,1:12:44.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇軍出動過百艘反潛艇戰機 還有潛艇和海面艦隊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.12,1:12:44.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Russians have attack subs and surface groups here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.13,1:12:48.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 火力強大 - 但他們是拯救隊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.13,1:12:48.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's a lot of firepower. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.67,1:12:55.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一件怪事 他們作聲納探測 但不理探測結果
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.67,1:12:55.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And there's something else strange. They're not listening to their sonar.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.35,1:13:00.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思? 以時速30海裡航行 根本無法探聽任何聲響
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.35,1:13:00.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,At 30 knots, they could run over my daughter's stereo and not hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.19,1:13:07.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們不是找韋莫斯 他們驅趕他
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.19,1:13:07.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They're not trying to find Ramius, they're trying to drive him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.99,1:13:12.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,趕到敵人的地盤
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.99,1:13:12.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hounds to the hunters.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.99,1:13:17.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷先生 這艦長的確會去美國
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.99,1:13:17.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Your sub captain is going to make it to America.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.58,1:13:20.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他將會在抵岸前身亡
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.58,1:13:20.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's going to die within sight of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.91,1:13:25.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他的僚機要求准許發炮
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.91,1:13:25.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,His wingman requested permission to fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.79,1:13:30.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,若有人輕舉妄動 我們會捲入大戰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.79,1:13:30.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This could be the biggest naval battle since Jutland. Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.13,1:13:36.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 水溫太低 不能沖進水裡 - 嘗試登上甲板
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.13,1:13:36.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The water's too cold to eject. - Try and bring him aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.26,1:13:40.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,請問這是什麼潛艇?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.26,1:13:40.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's this sub off by herself? Bart Mancuso's boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.56,1:13:43.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,馬拔的潛艇會趕去"紅航線一號"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.56,1:13:43.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's at the bottom of Red Route One.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.02,1:13:48.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他的電腦發現"岩漿移位"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.02,1:13:48.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's contacted what his computer calls magma displacement.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.73,1:13:52.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他有… 岩漿移位?  那是地震學的問題?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.73,1:13:52.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Magma displacement? Is that like a seismic anomaly?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.99,1:13:58.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可否讓我登上達拉斯號?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.99,1:13:58.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I suppose so. Can you get me on board the Dallas?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.78,1:14:04.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 馬艦長已經找到赤色十月 - 他沒找到什麼 他在等候
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.78,1:14:04.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Mancuso found the Red October. - He hasn't found anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.75,1:14:09.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,無聲推進系統經常被誤認為…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.75,1:14:09.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This silent propulsion system could be mistaken for...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.59,1:14:13.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,傑克 只能坐直升機去達拉斯號
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.59,1:14:13.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The only way to get you out there is by chopper.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.22,1:14:18.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,直升機可沒有這麼多燃料
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.22,1:14:18.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'd have to strip it down into a flying gas can.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.30,1:14:23.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,拯救揚基一號的部隊 準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.30,1:14:23.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yankee One is on final. Rescue personnel are in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.52,1:14:26.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,提升左翼
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.52,1:14:26.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Pick up your left wing.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.40,1:14:28.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,禁止著陸…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.40,1:14:28.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Power! Wave off!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.94,1:14:31.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,機師彈出機艙…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.94,1:14:31.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Eject!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.25,1:14:50.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,飛行甲板著火 各單位合作救火
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.25,1:14:50.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This business will get out of control and we'll be lucky to live through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.68,1:15:07.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,達拉斯可能會離開原地點
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.68,1:15:07.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's enough fuel to get you there, but the Dallas may not be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.10,1:15:13.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會跟它聯絡 但它可能下潛了 如果你要跳傘…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.10,1:15:13.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She might have gone deep. If you have to ditch...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.62,1:15:25.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果要跳傘 記得拿救生裝備
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.62,1:15:25.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you have to ditch, get into the survival gear.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.50,1:15:30.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這種水溫 你只能支持四分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.50,1:15:30.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,At this water temperature, you'll have about four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.09,1:15:37.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,下次寫通告算了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.09,1:15:37.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Next time, Jack, write a memo.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.83,1:16:14.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 船長睡了?  - 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.83,1:16:14.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Is the captain sacked out? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.71,1:16:19.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他呢?  -  他不肯睡
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.71,1:16:19.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What about him? - He won't leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.73,1:16:32.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我見過美人魚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.73,1:16:32.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, I've seen a mermaid once.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.15,1:16:37.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,還見過鯊魚吃八爪魚
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.15,1:16:37.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I've even seen a shark eat an octopus.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.23,1:16:41.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但沒見過鬼魅一般的蘇聯潛艇
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.23,1:16:41.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,But I've never seen a phantom Russian submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.11,1:17:27.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會探測情況 在數分鐘後轉變方向
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.11,1:17:27.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're emerging from the route. We'll make the first turn shortly.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.24,1:17:33.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,履帶運作回復正常
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.24,1:17:33.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The caterpillar is operational and appears to be running normally.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.50,1:17:39.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,內奸的事令船員人心惶惶
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.50,1:17:39.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The crew know about the saboteur and they are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.30,1:17:45.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可以在適當時機利用這心態
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.30,1:17:45.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That could be useful when the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.60,1:17:53.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,十六小時後 會到達拉布拉多海岸
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.60,1:17:53.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We could make the Labrador coast in 16 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:17:56.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,那裡太冷 船員會冷死
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.19,1:17:56.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Half of them would freeze before they were rescued.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.98,1:18:01.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,四十八小時後 到麻塞諸塞或緬因州
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.98,1:18:01.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's Massachusetts or Maine in 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.19,1:18:04.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,兩天
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.19,1:18:04.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.95,1:18:16.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們會不會讓我住在蒙大拿州
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.95,1:18:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you think they will let me live in Montana?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.42,1:18:26.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你想住哪裡都可以
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.42,1:18:26.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I would think they'll let you live wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.68,1:18:32.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我會住在蒙大拿州
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.68,1:18:32.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Good, then I will live in Montana.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.27,1:18:37.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,娶一個肥胖的美國妻子 養兔子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.27,1:18:37.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I will marry a round American woman and raise rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.23,1:18:40.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她會給我燒飯
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.23,1:18:40.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And she will cook them for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:44.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我會買一輛小貨車
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:44.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I will have a pickup truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.74,1:18:51.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可能買一輛旅遊車
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.74,1:18:51.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Or possibly even a recreational vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.20,1:18:55.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開著旅遊車穿州過省
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.20,1:18:55.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,and drive from state to state.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.37,1:18:59.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 可以這樣做? - 是
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.37,1:18:59.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do they let you do that? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.67,1:19:04.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 不必申請? - 無須申請 穿州過省
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.67,1:19:04.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- No papers? - No papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.51,1:19:07.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開始轉方向
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.51,1:19:07.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Commence your turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.80,1:19:16.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,冬天住在亞利桑那州
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.80,1:19:16.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In winter, I will live in Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.14,1:19:22.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我需要兩個妻子 - 至少兩個
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.14,1:19:22.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I think I will need two wives. - At least.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.41,1:19:39.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 目標可能想轉方向 - 指揮台 目標可能進行急轉
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.41,1:19:39.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Possible aspect change on target. - Concur, change in bearing rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.63,1:19:46.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 指揮台 "瘋狂伊凡" - 停止 肅靜 停止
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.63,1:19:46.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Crazy Ivan! - All stop. Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.56,1:20:01.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇軍有時會突然轉彎 看看有否被跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.56,1:20:01.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Russian subs turn suddenly when they want to see if anyone is behind them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.19,1:20:04.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是"瘋狂伊凡"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.19,1:20:04.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We call it Crazy Ivan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.69,1:20:10.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要關掉所有機器 銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.69,1:20:10.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You shut everything down and make like a hole in the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.20,1:20:16.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 還有什麼問題?  - 大船不能一下子停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.20,1:20:16.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's the catch? - A boat this big doesn't stop on a dime.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.00,1:20:22.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可能會被捲進他們的船尾
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.00,1:20:22.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If we're too close, we'll drift right into the back of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.63,1:20:28.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你有什麼心願?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.63,1:20:28.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What about you? What do you look forward to?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.35,1:20:42.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我再沒有這種心情
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.35,1:20:42.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have no such appetites.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.02,1:20:46.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,看看他們能否聽見我們
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.02,1:20:46.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's see if he can hear us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.57,1:20:54.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一定還有事情想做
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.57,1:20:54.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There must be something.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.00,1:21:05.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.00,1:21:05.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.30,1:21:11.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我懷念小時候…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.30,1:21:11.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I miss the peace of fishing.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.09,1:21:15.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,寧靜地釣魚的日子
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.09,1:21:15.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Like when I was a boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.35,1:21:23.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,四十年來 我一直航海
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.35,1:21:23.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,40 years I've been at sea. A war at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.98,1:21:32.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,海上的戰爭 一場沒有戰役的戰爭 沒有紀念碑
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.98,1:21:32.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A war with no battles. No monuments.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.16,1:21:36.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,只有死傷者
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.16,1:21:36.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Only casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.95,1:21:43.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,妻子在結婚當日 變成寡婦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.95,1:21:43.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I widowed her the day I married her.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.04,1:21:50.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,她去世的時候 我還在船上
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.04,1:21:50.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My wife died while I was at sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.23,1:22:12.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,找人看守機器艙
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.23,1:22:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Post guards in the engineering spaces.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.49,1:22:17.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,弄壞履帶的人 會作出更嚴重的破壞
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.49,1:22:17.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If he can get to the caterpillar, he can get to somewhere more vital.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.24,1:22:25.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 潛艇在哪裡?  - 指揮台 目標在右舷
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.24,1:22:25.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where is he Jonesy? - Target is on our starboard side.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.04,1:22:30.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他想回到原來的路線
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.04,1:22:30.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My read is that he's returning to base course.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.55,1:22:36.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他回到航線210 - 他環繞我們
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.55,1:22:36.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Concur, he's returning to 210. - He went right around us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.43,1:22:41.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,等三十秒 然後以無聲系統推進
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.43,1:22:41.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give him another 30 seconds. Then secure from silent running.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.64,1:22:46.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 收到傳訊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.64,1:22:46.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Here's what we got on the ELF.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.23,1:22:50.82,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.23,1:22:50.82,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.99,1:23:01.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.99,1:23:01.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.99,1:23:05.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.99,1:23:05.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You're not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.38,1:23:21.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要及早折返 達拉斯沒收到指示
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.38,1:23:21.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're approaching no return. Dallas probably didn't get the message.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.89,1:23:26.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我們要回母艦 - 再等一會 不行 燃料不夠
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.89,1:23:26.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We have to turn back. - Give it a couple more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.52,1:23:30.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你們沒有後備燃料?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.52,1:23:30.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You've got a reserve fuel tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.81,1:23:34.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我有十分鐘後備燃料 但只有作戰時才可動用
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.81,1:23:34.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I've got a ten minute reserve. I can't invade that except in time of war.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.11,1:23:39.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你不讓我上潛艇 戰爭會爆發
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.11,1:23:39.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you don't get me on that sub, that's what you'll have.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.03,1:23:44.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,聽到嗎? 我們再等十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.03,1:23:44.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you've got ten minutes of fuel, we stay here ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.71,1:23:53.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備工具 東面兩哩外有潛艇
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.71,1:23:53.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I've got a submarine at three o'clock. About two miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.51,1:24:00.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 好 給他戴上工具 - 我們把你放到潛艇下面去
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.51,1:24:00.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Okay, hook him up. - I'll be lowering you down to the sub.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.34,1:24:05.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,希望這東西…能把煙當作燃料
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.34,1:24:05.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's hope this thing runs on fumes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.31,1:24:11.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,浮上海面 是  這傢伙要吃苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.31,1:24:11.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Surface the ship. This guy is in for a hell of a ride.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.36,1:24:14.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 坐下來
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.36,1:24:14.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, Commander, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.03,1:24:20.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 有經驗嗎?  - 在夏威夷試過 當時風平浪靜
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.03,1:24:20.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Did you ever do this before? - Once, on a calm day.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.36,1:24:23.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,直升機無法穩定地飛行
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.36,1:24:23.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The pilot will have trouble keeping it steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.12,1:24:27.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,拿著這東西 避免電擊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.12,1:24:27.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't get grounded with that rod.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.45,1:24:32.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,旋翼的靜電 能燃亮芝加哥城
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.45,1:24:32.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The rotors will be putting out enough static to light up Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.17,1:24:36.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,當海軍就是這樣 我預備了潛水夫 他可能會墜海
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.17,1:24:36.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I've got a diver ready in case this guy goes in the drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.80,1:24:40.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對 這瘋子想玩命
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.80,1:24:40.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Who would go for a stunt like this!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.91,1:25:08.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,記著 如果我要把你帶上來
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.91,1:25:08.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If I've got to bring you back up, I'll shake the wire.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.00,1:25:13.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我會搖繩子和豎起大拇指 兩手交抱
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.00,1:25:13.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll give you a thumbs up. Remember to cross your arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.04,1:25:17.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,行嗎?  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.04,1:25:17.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, out you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.39,1:25:28.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,乘客在半空中往前蕩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.39,1:25:28.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's halfway down. You're drifting forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.35,1:25:35.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,湯姆 勾著他的繩
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.35,1:25:35.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get the hook on his cable.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.86,1:25:39.90,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,勾他的繩 小心 別碰他 他來了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.86,1:25:39.90,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Watch it! Don't touch him. Okay, here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.78,1:25:51.12,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,風太大了 他在哪裡? 見不到他
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.78,1:25:51.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It'd be easier without that crosswind. I can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.58,1:25:56.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別碰他
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.58,1:25:56.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.05,1:26:05.64,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 行不通  - 拉他回來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.05,1:26:05.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- This is never going to work. - Reel him back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.60,1:26:15.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.60,1:26:15.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.36,1:26:21.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,達拉斯號 有沒有準備潛水夫?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.36,1:26:21.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dallas, have you got a swimmer?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.44,1:26:26.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,停船 有人在左舷墜海 派出潛水夫
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.44,1:26:26.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Man overboard, port side. Send out the diver.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.24,1:26:30.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,達拉斯號 我們要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.24,1:26:30.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dallas, we are history.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.79,1:26:42.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,救下麵那位博士 我去逃生艙
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.79,1:26:42.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get the doc down here. I'll be in the escape trunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.18,1:26:49.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,拿梯子來…打開艙蓋
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.18,1:26:49.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Down ladder. Make a hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.74,1:27:09.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你好嗎? 我很高興能上船
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.74,1:27:09.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How do you do, Captain? It's a pleasure to be aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.74,1:27:15.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我要跟總統說話
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.74,1:27:15.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have to talk to the President.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.58,1:27:19.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好的 請問所為何事?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.58,1:27:19.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Of course. May I enquire as to the subject?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.84,1:27:27.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,看來我們的潛艇沒有失蹤
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.84,1:27:27.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My report of a missing submarine was not completely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.55,1:27:34.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,該艘潛艇由韋莫斯艦長指揮
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.55,1:27:34.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The submarine in question is commanded by Marko Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.98,1:27:40.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他陷入精神崩潰的狀態
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.98,1:27:40.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Apparently he has suffered a mental or nervous breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.98,1:27:48.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在出發前 他給巴度甯上將
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.98,1:27:48.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Just before he sailed, he posted a letter to Admiral Padorin
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.41,1:27:51.28,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,寄去了一封信
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.41,1:27:51.28,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,in which he announced his intention...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.49,1:27:56.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他想向美國發射導彈
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.49,1:27:56.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...to fire his missiles on the USA.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.21,1:28:00.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,上次為什麼不告訴我?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.21,1:28:00.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Why didn't you tell me this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.13,1:28:05.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,莫斯科不會向我說明一切事情
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.13,1:28:05.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Moscow does not always tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.96,1:28:10.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的潛艇艦長瘋了?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.96,1:28:10.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,So one of your submarine captains has gone insane?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.93,1:28:17.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你想怎樣?  - 你們願意幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.93,1:28:17.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You offered your assistance. - You want us to help you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.02,1:28:24.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,本來是拯救他 現在要追殺他?  我奉命來請貴國總統幫忙
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.02,1:28:24.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I have been instructed to ask your president for precisely that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.23,1:28:29.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,已經找到他 但我們要為你停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.23,1:28:29.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'd already found him. We had to break off to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.78,1:28:34.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 抽煙嗎?  - 不
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.78,1:28:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Coffee. A cigarette? - I don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.20,1:28:39.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,假設我們找到他 然後怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.20,1:28:39.00,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Assuming we can find him, what am I supposed to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.16,1:28:43.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,收到緊急訊號
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.16,1:28:43.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're receiving flash traffic on the emergency circuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.59,1:28:45.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,把它翻譯
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.59,1:28:45.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bring it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.34,1:28:50.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷先生
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.34,1:28:50.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, Mr. Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:56.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我們要單獨談 - 利昂 過來
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:56.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Chief, excuse us for a second. - Come on, Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.69,1:29:08.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在追蹤赤色十月 艦長是韋莫斯
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.69,1:29:08.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The sub is named the Red October, under the command of Marko Ramius.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.86,1:29:14.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他和部分手下可能想變節
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.86,1:29:14.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's the possibility that he and some of the crew want to defect.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.83,1:29:19.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,變節?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.83,1:29:19.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Defect?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.91,1:29:22.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.91,1:29:22.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.52,1:29:43.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,那潛艇叫赤色十月? 是 艦長是韋莫斯 是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.52,1:29:43.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The boat's the Red October? The skipper's Ramius?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.94,1:29:49.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,形勢轉變了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.94,1:29:49.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It seems that circumstances have changed somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.07,1:30:00.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,給他幹衣服 我在指揮台 是
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.07,1:30:00.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get this man some dry clothes. I'll be in the conn.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.37,1:30:05.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"總指揮部宣佈 蘇軍潛艇赤色十月
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.37,1:30:05.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Soviet submarine Red October under the command of Marko Ramius
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.29,1:30:10.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,其艦長韋莫斯 準備擅自發射飛彈
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.29,1:30:10.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,reported as potential renegade. Threat of independent missile launch."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.21,1:30:16.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你有權採用任何行動 防止此軍艦接近美國海岸"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.21,1:30:16.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Use any necessary force to prevent its approach to the United States."
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.94,1:30:35.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,左轉10度 航道265
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.94,1:30:35.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Left 10 degrees rudder. Steer course 265.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.70,1:30:42.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發出緊急訊號
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.70,1:30:42.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Chief of the Watch, rig for red.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.88,1:30:57.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼事? - 我們準備好作戰 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.88,1:30:57.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's going on? - Battle stations are manned and ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.01,1:31:04.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 我要跟你談談 - 現在不行 潛至一千二百英尺 俯傾二十度
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.01,1:31:04.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain, I have to talk to you. - Not now. Take her to 1,200 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.39,1:31:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,潛至一千二百英尺 俯傾二十度
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.39,1:31:09.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Diving officer, make your depth 1,200 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.90,1:31:15.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,全速下潛… 俯傾二十度 俯傾二十度 是
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.90,1:31:15.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Full dive on fair water planes. Full dive on stern planes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.66,1:31:22.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,四百五十英尺 潛至一千二百英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.66,1:31:22.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Passing 450 feet, going to 1,200.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.66,1:31:25.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,五百英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.66,1:31:25.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,500.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.79,1:31:29.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,六百英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.79,1:31:29.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,600.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.75,1:31:33.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,七百英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.75,1:31:33.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,700.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.84,1:31:40.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 一切順利?  - 是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.84,1:31:40.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Did you get a good fix? - Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.06,1:31:52.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 鐘斯 找到他嗎?  - 很微弱…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.06,1:31:52.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Sonar, have you got him yet, Jonesy? - Very faint, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.57,1:31:58.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在航道250 找到颱風七號
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.57,1:31:58.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, contact on 250. Right where he's supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.24,1:32:02.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他有否發覺我們? - 沒有
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.24,1:32:02.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Is he alerted to our presence? - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.95,1:32:08.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,左轉到265 溜到他們背後
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.95,1:32:08.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come left to 265. Bring us up behind him quietly.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.21,1:32:10.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,再下潛五百英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.21,1:32:10.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Make your depth 500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.97,1:32:23.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 讓我說兩分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.97,1:32:23.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Please listen to me. Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.39,1:32:29.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 何時能進入它的航道 - 四分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.39,1:32:29.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Time to intercept his track? - Four minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.81,1:32:33.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 給你兩分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.81,1:32:33.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very well, Mr. Ryan. Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.74,1:32:43.66,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,那些指示很合理 但實情是…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.74,1:32:43.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I understand that message, it makes perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.83,1:32:48.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,韋莫斯想變節 所以蘇軍一直想擊沉他
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.83,1:32:48.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ramius intends to defect. The Russians are trying to sink him.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.66,1:32:53.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 但他們無能為力 - 發炮程式準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.66,1:32:53.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- They haven't been able to. - I have a firing solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.34,1:32:57.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇軍想盡方法阻止韋莫斯變節
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.34,1:32:57.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Russians will stop at nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.71,1:33:03.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們想我們擊沉他 所以說他瘋了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.71,1:33:03.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,They invented this story because they need our help to sink him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.76,1:33:11.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,啟動保安系統 我不想他反過來對付我們
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.76,1:33:11.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Weapons control, full safety. I don't want this fish coming back at us.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.48,1:33:14.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 我認識這個人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.48,1:33:14.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I know this man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.77,1:33:21.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他有沒有做"瘋狂伊凡"?  下一次是右轉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.77,1:33:21.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Has he made any Crazy Ivans? His next one will be to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.86,1:33:26.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,因為上一次是左轉?  因為過了三十分 他總會右轉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.86,1:33:26.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He always goes to starboard in the bottom half of the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.62,1:33:32.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,調整魚雷管 準備發炮
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.62,1:33:32.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Flood tubes one and two.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.67,1:33:37.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,跟他聯絡 那不算是違反命令 他想變節
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.67,1:33:37.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You have to establish contact. He wants to defect!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.38,1:33:42.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,叫霍生送槍械來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.38,1:33:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Call Chief Watson to the conn with his sidearm.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.31,1:33:50.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,目標可能會移動
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.31,1:33:50.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Possible aspect change in target.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.98,1:33:54.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,目標可能會移動
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.98,1:33:54.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Concur, change in bearing rate.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.48,1:33:58.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,指揮台 "瘋狂伊凡"
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.48,1:33:58.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Crazy Ivan!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.78,1:34:05.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 他轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.78,1:34:05.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain, he's turning.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.74,1:34:12.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他向哪邊轉 - 右轉
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.74,1:34:12.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Which way is he turning? - To the starboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.75,1:34:16.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,給他一個機會
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.75,1:34:16.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give the man a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.38,1:34:21.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 全速後退 - 再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.38,1:34:21.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- All back full. - Say again.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.47,1:34:24.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 全速後退 - 是的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.47,1:34:24.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- All back full! - Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.56,1:34:35.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 水裡形成空洞 他會聽見我們 - 停下來
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.56,1:34:35.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're cavitating! He can hear us. - All stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.23,1:34:38.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們暴露了行蹤
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.23,1:34:38.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We just unzipped our fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.94,1:34:44.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開啟外門 準備開火
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.94,1:34:44.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Open the outer door. Firing point procedures.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.28,1:34:48.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他有任何異動 我會立刻發炮
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.28,1:34:48.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If the bastard twitches, I'm going to blow him to Mars.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.58,1:34:51.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,停止…
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.58,1:34:51.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.50,1:34:54.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,能否辨認對方?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.50,1:34:54.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can you identify the contact?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.04,1:35:00.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,美國洛杉磯級潛艇 位置是015
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.04,1:35:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Los Angeles class attack sub. Bearing: 015. Range: 300 meters.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.46,1:35:03.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 他可能想打開魚雷管道
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.46,1:35:03.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Opening torpedo tube doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.34,1:35:06.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,外門開啟了 準備開火
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.34,1:35:06.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Outer doors open. Ready to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.72,1:35:11.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我的命令很明確
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.72,1:35:11.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very well. My orders are specific.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.39,1:35:14.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他開了外門 準備開火
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.39,1:35:14.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He is preparing to fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.64,1:35:19.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,調整三號和四號魚雷管 準備開火
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.64,1:35:19.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Flood tubes three and four and plot a solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.78,1:35:24.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要打開魚雷管的門?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.78,1:35:24.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Shall I open the torpedo tube doors?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.41,1:35:32.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 要開啟外門嗎?  - 不
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.41,1:35:32.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Shall I open the outer doors? - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.91,1:35:36.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,用電腦記下發炮程式
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.91,1:35:36.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Lock the firing solution into the computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.87,1:35:39.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不要開門
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.87,1:35:39.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not open the doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.22,1:35:52.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 艦長 用電腦記下發炮程式
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.22,1:35:52.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, Captain. Lock solution into computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.35,1:35:57.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 目標準備了魚雷管  - 他有沒有開外門?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.35,1:35:57.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Target has flooded his tubes. - Has he opened his outer doors?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.56,1:36:01.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有 他按兵不動
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.56,1:36:01.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Negative. He just sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.48,1:36:07.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 慢著 目標在往上浮升 - 那是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.48,1:36:07.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Target is coming shallow. - What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.45,1:36:12.62,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這位蘇聯人很聰明
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.45,1:36:12.62,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It means he's a very cool customer.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.78,1:36:18.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他不想煽動我們發炮 他升上水面視察情況
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.78,1:36:18.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He knows we're ready to shoot. He's heading for the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.50,1:36:22.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他在什麼航道?  - 航道是270 向著西面
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.50,1:36:22.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's his course now? - 270. Due west.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.84,1:36:26.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們靠近他 是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.84,1:36:26.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bring us alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.34,1:36:29.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,聲納有其他發現嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.34,1:36:29.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sonar, report all contacts.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.55,1:36:33.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,只有颱風七號 位置是195
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.55,1:36:33.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My only contact is Typhoon 7.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.10,1:36:39.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 好 目標在哪種射程之內?  - 三百碼之內
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.10,1:36:39.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Range to target? - Range is 300 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.56,1:36:44.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,上升至六十五英尺
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.56,1:36:44.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Make your depth 65 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.15,1:36:50.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他想上水面看清楚 我們奉陪
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.15,1:36:50.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He wants to go up and take a peek. We'll play along.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.30,1:37:12.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,武器情況如何? 準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.30,1:37:12.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Weapons status?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.76,1:37:17.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷管準備好了 外門沒打開
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.76,1:37:17.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Tubes three and four are flooded, but outer doors are closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.78,1:37:36.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,要跟他說話嗎? 他出現了 你打算說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.78,1:37:36.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You wanted to talk to him. What do you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.20,1:37:40.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是他在看望遠鏡? 可能吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.20,1:37:40.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Will he be the only one looking through the periscope?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.58,1:37:43.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我要冒險一試
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.58,1:37:43.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll have to chance that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.08,1:37:48.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"聽說閣下想發射導彈"
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.08,1:37:48.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"US told you intend missile launch."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.42,1:37:53.84,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"別接近美國 否則我們會進攻"
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.42,1:37:53.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Do not approach US coast or you will be attacked."
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.01,1:37:59.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"如果另有意圖 可否一起商議"
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.01,1:37:59.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"If intention is other, will you discuss option?"
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.06,1:38:03.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他可否以一下聲響示意?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.06,1:38:03.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Can he acknowledge with a single ping?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.48,1:38:07.52,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可以 但他會否答覆?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.48,1:38:07.52,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He can. The question is, will he?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.11,1:38:19.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,表明射程範圍 一下聲響
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.11,1:38:19.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Verify our range to target. One ping only.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.16,1:38:23.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.16,1:38:23.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.34,1:38:32.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的 現在怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.34,1:38:32.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll be damned. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.05,1:38:39.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好 "如要變節…"
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.05,1:38:39.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. "If defection..."
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.85,1:38:50.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我要地圖
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.85,1:38:50.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Chart. I need a chart.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.61,1:38:57.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在哪裡?  一個水深的地方…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.61,1:38:57.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Where the hell are we? Someplace deep.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.83,1:39:03.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.83,1:39:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, send him this.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.75,1:39:11.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你瘋了嗎?  - 照辦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.75,1:39:11.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you out of your mind? - Just send it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.30,1:39:19.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,告訴我 你怎知道他會右轉
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.30,1:39:19.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How did you know he was going to go to starboard?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.68,1:39:25.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道 我想碰碰運氣來打斷你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.68,1:39:25.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't. I had a 50-50 chance and I needed a break. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.98,1:39:30.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,不要緊 很久沒使用摩斯密碼
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.98,1:39:30.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's all right. My Morse is so rusty,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.65,1:39:35.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我可能發出了美女三圍數字
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.65,1:39:35.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I may be sending him dimensions on playmate of the month.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.80,1:39:57.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,再次表明射程範圍
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.80,1:39:57.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Reverify our range to target.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.26,1:40:01.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 一下聲響 - 艦長 我剛…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.26,1:40:01.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- One ping only. - Captain, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.93,1:40:06.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,請再發出一下聲響
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.93,1:40:06.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Give me a ping, Vassily. One ping only, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.23,1:40:11.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.23,1:40:11.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Aye, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.49,1:40:18.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.49,1:40:18.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell is this about?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.91,1:40:24.66,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可能真的要擊沉他
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.91,1:40:24.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Russians want us to sink her. We might have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.38,1:40:36.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要給美國人一點迴旋餘地
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.38,1:40:36.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We must give this American a wide berth.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.42,1:40:41.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,轉向南邊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.42,1:40:41.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Let us turn south.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.73,1:40:45.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(勞倫深淵)
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.39,1:40:55.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,卡馬夫先生  計畫路線 往南走
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.39,1:40:55.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Mr. Kamarov, plot a new course due south.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.03,1:41:00.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是 新航道180
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.03,1:41:00.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,New course: 180.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.67,1:41:30.00,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(大淺灘 勞倫深淵以北 二十小時後)
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.73,1:41:38.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,反應器故障 關閉反應器
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.73,1:41:38.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Shut down the reactor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.24,1:41:43.20,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 封閉通風系統 - 通風系統壞了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.24,1:41:43.20,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Seal the ventilation system. - The ventilation controls have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.37,1:41:47.66,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,所有人離開這裡 出去
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.37,1:41:47.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Everybody out! Clear the compartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.09,1:42:02.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 關掉通風系統 - 控制器沒反應
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.09,1:42:02.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Shut the ventilation system down. - The controls don't respond.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.72,1:42:06.43,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,用人手把它關閉 關掉它
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.72,1:42:06.43,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Bypass it. Seal it manually. Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.76,1:42:10.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.76,1:42:10.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Say again.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.48,1:42:23.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,輻射外泄 我們要關閉反應器 通風系統失靈了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.48,1:42:23.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We suffered a leak in the cooling tube. The ventilation circuits are disabled.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.66,1:42:28.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 冷卻劑似乎受了污染 - 我早知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.66,1:42:28.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The coolant is contaminated. - I knew it was damaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.16,1:42:34.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,所有部門都發出輻射警號
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.16,1:42:34.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Radiation alarms are activated in all compartments.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.67,1:42:39.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,浮上水面 輸入新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.67,1:42:39.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get us to periscope depth. We'll ventilate with outside air.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.92,1:42:44.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,換氣是不夠的 我們要疏散船員
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.92,1:42:44.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Ventilating won't do anything. Get the men off.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.43,1:42:48.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 電池可維持多久?  - 四小時 最長六小時
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.43,1:42:48.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What is the battery condition? - Four hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.51,1:42:53.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 啟動電池系統 - 這是一級輻射洩漏
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.51,1:42:53.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Engage battery system. - The whole ship is contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.02,1:42:57.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要疏散船員
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.02,1:42:57.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We've got to get the men off.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.65,1:43:00.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 有人蓄意毀壞潛艇
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.65,1:43:00.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sir, we have been sabotaged.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.90,1:43:04.36,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 誰說有人蓄意毀壞?  - 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.90,1:43:04.36,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Who said anything about sabotage? - Captain!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.53,1:43:07.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 醫生可能說得對
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.53,1:43:07.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm afraid the doctor is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.29,1:43:17.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 浮上水面 疏散船員
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.29,1:43:17.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very well. Surface. We'll evacuate the men to the deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.04,1:43:23.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,浮上水面 準備召集船員 到逃生艙口
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.04,1:43:23.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Surface the ship. Muster all personnel to escape hatches.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.30,1:43:30.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,把救生艇綁在艙面 以救生艇作庇護 等待艦隊救援
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.30,1:43:30.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Break out the rafts. We'll use them as shelters until the fleet arrives.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.22,1:44:17.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,點算人數 不能留下船員
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.22,1:44:17.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Make sure the count is accurate. We must get the entire crew out.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.10,1:44:25.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,救生艇綁好 正在疏散船員
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.10,1:44:25.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Master at Arms reports rafts secure and evacuation proceeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.57,1:44:38.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,軍官不會逗留超過二十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.57,1:44:38.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,No officer will spend more than 20 minutes below deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.71,1:44:44.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發現船隻 在六哩外 正在駛近
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.71,1:44:44.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Surface contact: 270. Six miles and closing fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.96,1:44:48.84,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是戰艦 - 什麼戰艦?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.96,1:44:48.84,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's a warship! - Here? Can you identify?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.01,1:44:54.68,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是美軍驅逐艦 它在發訊號
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.01,1:44:54.68,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a US frigate. Probably Perry class. He's signaling.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.85,1:45:00.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"赤色十月…" "停止航行"
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.85,1:45:00.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Red October, halt and stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.77,1:45:04.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別嘗試下潛 否則我們會發炮
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.77,1:45:04.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not attempt to submerge or you will be fired upon.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.03,1:45:09.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 他們想登艇
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.03,1:45:09.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He means to board us.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.08,1:45:21.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟船員離開 我和軍官摧毀潛艇 沉沒深海
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.08,1:45:21.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You will go with the crew. The officers and I will submerge beneath you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.88,1:45:27.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我們要摧毀艦  - 你會得到列寧勳章
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.88,1:45:27.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We'll scuttle the ship. - You will receive the Order of Lenin.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.14,1:45:42.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們離船 艦長跟潛艇一起沉沒
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.14,1:45:42.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Prepare to cast off. The captain is going to scuttle the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.53,1:45:51.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他下潛了 - 發炮掠過艦頭 回航道180
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.53,1:45:51.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's going down, sir. - Put a shot across his bow.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.35,1:46:25.11,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,海克一號 這是指揮部
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.35,1:46:25.11,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Seahawk One, this is Bravo Command.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.67,1:46:46.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.67,1:46:46.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,She's ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.09,1:46:49.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,海克一號 準備發射 現在發射
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.09,1:46:49.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Release on my command.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.23,1:47:05.77,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,離開目標九百碼  八百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.23,1:47:05.77,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Range to target 900 yards... 800 yards...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.02,1:47:13.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,七百碼 六百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.02,1:47:13.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,700 yards... 600 yards...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.49,1:47:23.96,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,五百碼 四百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.49,1:47:23.96,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,500 yards... 400 yards...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.08,1:47:28.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,三百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.08,1:47:28.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,300 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.05,1:47:34.05,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷給引爆了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.05,1:47:34.05,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The torpedo is detonated.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.22,1:47:40.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,記著 那魚雷沒有自我毀滅 你聽到它撞向船身
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.22,1:47:40.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That torpedo did not self-destruct. You heard it hit the hull.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.97,1:47:44.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.97,1:47:44.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,And I was never here.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.10,1:47:50.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 通知達拉斯號 - 叫達拉斯號 派出深潛救助艇
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.10,1:47:50.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Give Dallas the go. - Get the DSRV moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.95,1:48:02.95,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這次行動隨時會出錯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.95,1:48:02.95,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Two million things can still go wrong with this stunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.12,1:48:08.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,中情局的人沒頭腦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.12,1:48:08.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Central Intelligence Agency... there's a contradiction in terms.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.84,1:48:12.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,咖啡味道如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.84,1:48:12.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How's the coffee, Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.84,1:48:18.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,達拉斯號 神秘號準備出發
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.84,1:48:18.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Dallas, this is the Mystic. Request clearance to launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.80,1:48:25.85,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艙口蓋好了 - 準備就緒 可以出發
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.80,1:48:25.85,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hatch is secured. - We're ready to launch.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.02,1:48:31.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 讓外周注水 是 - 外周注水完畢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.02,1:48:31.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Flood the skirt. - Skirt filled and equalized.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.57,1:48:35.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 可以出發 - 好 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.57,1:48:35.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ready to lift off. - Okay, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.61,1:48:41.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,離開母艦 推往左舷
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.61,1:48:41.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thrusting to port.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.22,1:49:07.31,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 距離六百碼  - 轉到075
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.22,1:49:07.31,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 600 yards and closing. - Steer right to course 075.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.27,1:49:17.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,兩百碼  一百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.27,1:49:17.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,200 yards... 100 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.87,1:49:27.45,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,開燈
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.87,1:49:27.45,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hit the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.68,1:49:43.10,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這傢伙真大
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.68,1:49:43.10,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus! That's a big sucker.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.28,1:50:03.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 好 位置正確 - 可以打開艙口
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.28,1:50:03.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Okay, we're in position. - You can open the hatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.70,1:50:10.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,等一會…鐘斯 懷先生
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.70,1:50:10.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Hold it a second. Jonesy... Mr. Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.58,1:50:18.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他想變節 - 他不會改變主意? 不會
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.58,1:50:18.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's defecting. - And he can't change his mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.05,1:50:24.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他不會改變主意 - 你敢以性命擔保?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.05,1:50:24.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's not going to change his mind. - Will you bet your life on that?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.16,1:50:47.53,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,請拿錘子給我 好
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.16,1:50:47.53,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sir, could you hand me that hammer?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.81,1:51:14.06,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,美國人
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.81,1:51:14.06,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Americans.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.45,1:52:56.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他臉色變青
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.45,1:52:56.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's turning green.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.81,1:53:18.64,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的西部牛仔
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.81,1:53:18.64,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's our buckaroo.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.81,1:53:23.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,笑什麼?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.81,1:53:23.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.23,1:53:27.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長說你像牛仔
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.23,1:53:27.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The captain thinks you're some sort of cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.40,1:53:35.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你懂俄語 - 一點點
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.40,1:53:35.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You speak Russian. - A little.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.24,1:53:41.38,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,知己知彼 百戰百勝 同意嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.24,1:53:41.38,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's wise to study the ways of one's adversary.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.54,1:53:43.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,說得對
Dialogue: 0,1:53:41.54,1:53:43.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.63,1:53:50.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在列寧格勒領事館見過面
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.63,1:53:50.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I doubt that you remember, but we met at the consulate in Leningrad.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.76,1:53:56.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,尊夫人的事 我很難過
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.76,1:53:56.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Along with your wife. I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.52,1:54:01.27,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼無故向我的船發炮?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.52,1:54:01.27,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What gives you the right to fire on my ship?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.44,1:54:05.69,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你的訊息沒有提及魚雷 - 懷
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.44,1:54:05.69,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You said nothing of a torpedo. - Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.94,1:54:12.57,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我要誤導你的船員 - 他們會獲救?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.94,1:54:12.57,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- We had to maintain the illusion. - Are my crew being rescued?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.74,1:54:16.70,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,拯救行動已開始
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.74,1:54:16.70,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,As we speak.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.83,1:54:23.92,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 是你發佈訊號的?  - 是
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.83,1:54:23.92,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You sent the signal? - That's correct, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.08,1:54:30.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎知道 我們的輻射意外是假的?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.08,1:54:30.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,How did you know that our reactor accident was false?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.17,1:54:33.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我循常理推測
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.17,1:54:33.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That was a guess, but it seemed logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.98,1:54:42.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.98,1:54:42.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.40,1:54:50.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我把導彈潛艇赤色十月交出來
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.40,1:54:50.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I present to you the ballistic missile submarine Red October.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.20,1:55:01.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我和軍官要求美國庇護
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.20,1:55:01.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My officers and I request asylum in the USA.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.12,1:55:09.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,幸會 我是達拉斯號的馬拔艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.12,1:55:09.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a pleasure, sir. Bart Mancuso, USS Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.80,1:55:17.26,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 魚雷 美國人再次發炮 - 聲調太高了 這是蘇聯魚雷
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.80,1:55:17.26,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Torpedo. The Americans are shooting. - The pitch is too high. It's Russian.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.93,1:55:21.18,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,還有魚雷? 從哪裡來?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.93,1:55:21.18,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Another torpedo?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.35,1:55:25.35,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發現蘇聯雅夫級潛艇
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.35,1:55:25.35,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sonar contact. Alfa class Soviet submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.69,1:55:35.32,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 為何不引爆?  - 魚雷偏離目標 擊不中赤色十月
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.69,1:55:35.32,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Why don't I have a detonation? - The weapon armed too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.49,1:55:39.54,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你計算錯誤 準備再發魚雷
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.49,1:55:39.54,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You had the wrong range. Fire again with the right setting.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.70,1:55:44.67,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,加強能源…叫救生艇離開
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.70,1:55:44.67,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Get me power, and get that damn thing off my boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.83,1:55:50.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 有人向我們發射魚雷 - 混帳 走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.83,1:55:50.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Somebody just shot at us. - No shit! Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.47,1:56:02.89,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長跟他們開戰
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.47,1:56:02.89,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The captain is fighting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.77,1:56:08.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,博列登 指揮射擊 是 艦長
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.77,1:56:08.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Borodin, fire control.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.15,1:56:13.99,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 懷 坐在這裡 - 我不是海軍 我是中情局人員
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.15,1:56:13.99,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ryan, sit here. - I'm not with the Navy. I'm CIA.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.15,1:56:18.37,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 中情局?  - 我不是特務 我為中情局著書
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.15,1:56:18.37,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- CIA? - I write books for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.66,1:56:22.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,坐下來 照我的吩咐做
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.66,1:56:22.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Sit down and do what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.91,1:56:26.42,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,蘇聯雅夫級潛艇 在右舷八千碼外
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.91,1:56:26.42,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Russian Alfa, 8,000 yards to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.58,1:56:32.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 看來是卡華洛夫號 - 加速
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.58,1:56:32.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I think it's the Konovalov. - Increase to flank.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.92,1:56:37.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,扭向右邊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:33.92,1:56:37.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That knob, turn right full.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.09,1:56:42.14,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 全速前進 轉右 - 他再次發炮
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.09,1:56:42.14,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- All ahead flank. Right full rudder. - He's shooting again.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.31,1:56:45.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備作戰
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.31,1:56:45.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.48,1:56:55.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 水裡有魚雷 位置是315 - 距離七千碼
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.48,1:56:55.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Torpedo in the water. Bearing 315. - Make range 7,000 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.36,1:57:01.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 向右轉 航道315 - 朝著魚雷沖過去?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:55.36,1:57:01.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Steer right 315. - That's heading into the torpedo.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.99,1:57:08.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 距離六千碼 - 向右轉 直至這裡寫著315
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.99,1:57:08.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Estimate range 6,000 yards. - Steer right 315.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.50,1:57:12.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷 千萬別轉方向 我們沖向魚雷
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.50,1:57:12.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That's wrong! Ryan, don't turn that wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.92,1:57:16.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,航道315
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.92,1:57:16.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,315.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.48,1:57:30.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 準備沖向魚雷 - 是
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.48,1:57:30.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- You're heading straight for it. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.77,1:57:34.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼? - 他沖向魚雷
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.77,1:57:34.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Doing what? - He's turning into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.94,1:57:40.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 赤色十月沖向魚雷 - 我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.94,1:57:40.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's directly in the torpedo's path. - Mother of God!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.20,1:57:44.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷在315 離我們五千碼
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.20,1:57:44.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo steady at 315. Range: 5,000 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.91,1:57:48.91,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 加速 - 不行 我們已推動至百分之一百一十
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.91,1:57:48.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- More speed. - We're already at 110%.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.08,1:57:54.71,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 那就增強至百分之一百一十五 - 距離三千碼 快來到了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.08,1:57:54.71,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Run at 115%. - Range: 3,000 yards and closing fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.43,1:58:07.47,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他想沖向魚雷自殺?  - 我們能否向蘇聯潛艇開火?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.43,1:58:07.47,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's heading right at the torpedo. - Can we shoot at the Russian Alfa?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.64,1:58:12.40,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他們沒有攻擊我們 我不能擅自開火
Dialogue: 0,1:58:07.64,1:58:12.40,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I can't attack a Soviet submarine without authorization.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.02,1:58:20.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷在315 距離是九百碼
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.02,1:58:20.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo steady at 315. Range: 900 yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.78,1:58:25.03,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷在二十秒後 命中目標
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.78,1:58:25.03,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo impact: 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.33,1:58:30.50,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 什麼書?  - 原諒我
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.33,1:58:30.50,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What books? - Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.66,1:58:36.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 你寫什麼書?  - 我寫過哈爾西上將的傳記
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.66,1:58:36.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What books did you write? - A biography on Admiral Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.34,1:58:42.93,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- "海軍戰士" 探討海軍戰略 - 我看過這本書
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.34,1:58:42.93,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's about naval combat tactics. - I know this book.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.09,1:58:47.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你的結論錯了 哈爾西策略失當
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.09,1:58:47.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Your conclusions were all wrong. Halsey acted stupidly.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.14,1:58:53.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,九、八、七、六...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:48.14,1:58:53.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Nine, eight, seven, six...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.40,1:58:59.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,...五、四、三、二...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.40,1:58:59.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,...five, four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.40,1:59:02.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷現在命中目標
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.40,1:59:02.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo impact now.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.00,1:59:15.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.00,1:59:15.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll be dammed.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.00,1:59:20.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 發生什麼事?  - 這是戰略
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.00,1:59:20.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened? - Combat tactics.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.67,1:59:26.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,射程縮短了 魚雷來不及引爆
Dialogue: 0,1:59:20.67,1:59:26.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The captain closed the distance before the torpedo could arm itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.89,1:59:29.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 沒事了?  - 不能這樣說
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.89,1:59:29.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's it? - Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.89,1:59:37.15,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,杜普夫艦長會解除武器安全系統
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.89,1:59:37.15,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Capt. Tupolev will be removing the safety features on all his weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.31,1:59:42.65,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他不會重蹈覆轍 發炮程式準備好了? - 艦長 初步計畫…
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.31,1:59:42.65,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Vassily, have you plotted a solution? - It's a little rough...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.16,1:59:52.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,槍聲
Dialogue: 0,1:59:49.16,1:59:52.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.45,1:59:56.29,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他不會改變主意? - 是船員作怪
Dialogue: 0,1:59:52.45,1:59:56.29,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He won't change his mind? - It's one of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.46,2:00:00.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,槍手不想變節
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.46,2:00:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Whoever he is, I'd say he's having second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.31,2:00:19.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我想看看蒙大拿
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.31,2:00:19.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I would like to have seen Montana.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.83,2:00:38.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 他跑進導彈庫 左邊發射井艙口出現警告訊號
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.83,2:00:38.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He's in the missile bay. We're showing a hatch warning on number 20.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.04,2:00:43.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他不能發炮 - 但能夠引爆導彈
Dialogue: 0,2:00:39.04,2:00:43.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He can't launch a missile? - No, but he can blow one up.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.42,2:00:50.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 你看守指揮台 射擊指揮中槍身亡 躲在他後面吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.42,2:00:50.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain, take the conn. Get in behind him and stay there.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.68,2:00:53.39,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,艦長 慢著
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.68,2:00:53.39,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Captain, wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.06,2:00:59.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你可能需要這個
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.06,2:00:59.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You may need this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.90,2:01:04.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.90,2:01:04.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.82,2:01:12.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別光站著 跟著他 你懂英語? 是 過來
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.82,2:01:12.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't just stand there, go with him! You, get your butt over here.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.95,2:01:19.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 魚雷失靈 - 該死的 解除安全系統
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.95,2:01:19.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- The torpedo broke up on impact. - Set the safety ranges for zero.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.79,2:01:24.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,千萬不能讓他破壞點火電路
Dialogue: 0,2:01:19.79,2:01:24.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We must get him before he gets to the ignition circuits.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.47,2:01:35.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,破壞點火電路會有何後果?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.47,2:01:35.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,What happens if he gets to the ignition circuits?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.18,2:01:38.19,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,他會焚毀整艘潛艇
Dialogue: 0,2:01:35.18,2:01:38.19,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,He can incinerate the ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.57,2:01:50.24,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 這裡只有這個出口?  - 是的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.57,2:01:50.24,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Is that the only way out of here? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.41,2:01:55.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 別讓他跑掉 - 懷
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.41,2:01:55.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Don't let him get past you. - Ryan...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.74,2:01:59.12,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,小心開槍
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.74,2:01:59.12,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be careful what you shoot at.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.29,2:02:04.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡有很多東西不能中彈
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.29,2:02:04.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Most things in here don't react too well to bullets.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.00,2:02:08.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.00,2:02:08.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Right.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.94,2:02:28.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,小心開槍?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.94,2:02:28.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Be careful what I shoot at?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.12,2:02:41.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 安全系統解除了 - 好 報告赤色十月的位置
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.12,2:02:41.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Safety ranges set to zero. - Where's Red October?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.37,2:02:47.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 它在我們後面 - 右轉 我會打敗他
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.37,2:02:47.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- She's behind us. - Right full rudder. I'll shake him loose.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.30,2:02:56.97,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 它在下潛 - 俯傾30度
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.30,2:02:56.97,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- He's going deep. - 30 degree down angle.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.14,2:02:59.81,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,反魚雷在那邊? 是的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.14,2:02:59.81,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Order counter measures.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.25,2:03:29.30,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,雅夫潛艇速度很快 他們逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.25,2:03:29.30,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The Alfa is too quick. It's only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.46,2:03:34.55,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,懷 這裡有很多東西不能中彈
Dialogue: 0,2:03:29.46,2:03:34.55,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"Some things in here don't react well to bullets..."
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.72,2:03:38.51,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,對 我也不能中彈
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.72,2:03:38.51,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.12,2:04:01.33,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 他在哪裡?  - 很接近
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.12,2:04:01.33,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where is he? - Close, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.25,2:04:06.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,距離九百米在正前方
Dialogue: 0,2:04:03.25,2:04:06.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,900 meters, directly ahead.  Got him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.92,2:04:10.09,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 行了 準備發射魚雷 - 射程太短了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:06.92,2:04:10.09,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Mark bearings and fire. - We are too close.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.25,2:04:15.63,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,別爭論 發射武器
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.25,2:04:15.63,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't argue with me. Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.14,2:04:20.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,又有魚雷 它會隨時爆炸
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.14,2:04:20.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Another torpedo, it went active as it was launched.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.76,2:04:25.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 它向我們沖過來 左轉 平衡艦首 - 魚雷鎖定我們了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.76,2:04:25.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Left full rudder. Ease her up. - I think he's got us.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.49,2:04:38.91,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,達拉斯 做得好
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.49,2:04:38.91,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Way to go, Dallas!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.66,2:04:47.79,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷在五百碼外沖過來 你成功了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.66,2:04:47.79,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Torpedo in acquisition. Range 500 yards. You've done it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.96,2:04:52.25,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,希望行得通 好了 浮上水面
Dialogue: 0,2:04:47.96,2:04:52.25,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I hope this works. Chief, put us on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.42,2:04:55.88,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,準備發射反魚雷 五、四…
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.42,2:04:55.88,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Counter measures on my mark. 5, 4...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.59,2:05:03.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,發放反魚雷 緊急引爆 全速上升
Dialogue: 0,2:04:58.59,2:05:03.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Release counter measures. Emergency blow. Full rise.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.90,2:05:14.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,六百英尺、五百英尺…
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.90,2:05:14.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,500 feet.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.65,2:05:18.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,快點上升
Dialogue: 0,2:05:14.65,2:05:18.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Big D. Fly!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.92,2:05:40.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷沒停下來 它尋找別的目標
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.92,2:05:40.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,That torpedo is still active. It's searching for another target.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.83,2:06:11.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然是廚師
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.83,2:06:11.04,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A goddamn cook.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.86,2:06:36.98,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,鎖定了我們
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.86,2:06:36.98,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's locked on us!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.15,2:06:42.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 雅夫潛艇離我們多近?  - 一千碼 在左舷
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.15,2:06:42.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- How close is that Alfa? - 1,000 yards dead astern.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.20,2:06:52.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,反方向轉 是 我們沖向敵方 魚雷跟著我們
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.20,2:06:52.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We're turning straight at him. The torpedo is still on our tail.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.34,2:07:01.13,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在適當的時候退開
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.34,2:07:01.13,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,The hard part about playing chicken is knowing when to flinch.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.51,2:07:10.56,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,距離400碼、350碼、300碼
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.51,2:07:10.56,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Collision in 400 yards, 350, 300...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.73,2:07:16.44,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 艦長 - 右轉 俯傾三十度
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.73,2:07:16.44,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain! - Right full rudder. 30 degree angle.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.61,2:07:20.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這次必定很驚險
Dialogue: 0,2:07:16.61,2:07:20.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This is going to be close.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.99,2:07:26.74,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,魚雷在前面 混蛋 你害死我們
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.99,2:07:26.74,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You arrogant ass, you've killed us.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.10,2:07:58.23,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們確定了赤色十月的位置
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.10,2:07:58.23,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We have ascertained the Red October's final position.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.86,2:08:04.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,但爆炸碎片遍佈深海
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.86,2:08:04.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Given the depth of the water and the spread of the wreckage,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.95,2:08:07.87,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要花一段時間調查
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.95,2:08:07.87,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,nothing has yet been recovered.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.03,2:08:13.66,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的人正在安排船員回國
Dialogue: 0,2:08:08.03,2:08:13.66,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Your people are with the crew and are making arrangements for their return.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.83,2:08:18.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,這是一場悲慘的意外
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.83,2:08:18.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,This has been a terrible tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.34,2:08:23.59,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,如果早點找我們 悲劇可能不會發生
Dialogue: 0,2:08:18.34,2:08:23.59,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,If you'd come to us earlier, it might have been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.68,2:08:30.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 我欣賞你坦誠的性格 - 彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.68,2:08:30.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- I appreciate your candor in this. - And I yours, Andrei.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.35,2:08:39.02,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可能將來有更先進的科技…來研究潛艇殘骸
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.35,2:08:39.02,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,In the future, technology may allow an investigation of the wreckage.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.19,2:08:43.07,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.19,2:08:43.07,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.36,2:08:53.75,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一件事 我難以啟齒…
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.36,2:08:53.75,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There is another matter, one that I'm reluctant to...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.25,2:09:02.34,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,直說無妨 一艘雅夫級潛艇 曾經在大淺灘出沒
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.25,2:09:02.34,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,One of our submarines, an Alfa, was last reported in the Grand Banks.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.50,2:09:06.76,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,它跟我們失去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.50,2:09:06.76,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,We've not heard from her for some time.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.05,2:09:12.60,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,又有潛艇失蹤?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.05,2:09:12.60,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,You've lost another submarine?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.51,2:09:25.04,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,(緬因州 佩諾布斯科特河)
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.99,2:09:31.49,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,長途跋涉來 把潛艇藏在河裡
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.99,2:09:31.49,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,All this way to hide a submarine in a river.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.70,2:09:38.83,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,離開海軍基地一百哩 衛星不會窺探這地方
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.70,2:09:38.83,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,It's 100 miles from any naval base. It's the last place a satellite will look.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.33,2:09:44.21,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這裡長大
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.33,2:09:44.21,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I grew up around here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.38,2:09:49.72,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,祖父在那個島 教我釣魚
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.38,2:09:49.72,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,My grandfather taught me to fish off that island over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.76,2:09:59.73,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你心裡還有一個疑問 為什麼不問?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.76,2:09:59.73,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There is one question you haven't asked me yet: Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.52,2:10:04.86,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,在適當的時候 你自然會說出來
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.52,2:10:04.86,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,I figured you would tell me when you were ready.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.78,2:10:12.41,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,有人說 我們要主動攻打美國
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.78,2:10:12.41,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There are those who believe we should attack the USA first.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.57,2:10:19.08,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,然後 一了百了 赤色十月就是為此而建造的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.57,2:10:19.08,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Settle everything in one moment. Red October was built for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.25,2:10:24.80,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,- 日後 莫斯科要付出沉重的代價 - 那可能是好事
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.25,2:10:24.80,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,- Now there'll be hell to pay in Moscow. - Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.96,2:10:28.17,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,或許會好起來
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.96,2:10:28.17,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe some good will come from it.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.34,2:10:34.01,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,一場小革命能整頓國家 不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.34,2:10:34.01,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,A little revolution now and then is a healthy thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.81,2:10:43.61,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,你仍然喜歡釣魚?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.81,2:10:43.61,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you still like to fish?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.02,2:10:48.94,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,維爾納斯有一條河流 跟這裡差不多
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.02,2:10:48.94,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,There's a river not unlike this near Vilnius,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.11,2:10:53.78,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,我祖父在那裡教我釣魚
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.11,2:10:53.78,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,where my grandfather taught me to fish.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.83,2:10:59.58,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"大海為每個人帶來新希望"
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.83,2:10:59.58,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"And the sea will grant each man new hope."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.75,2:11:03.46,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,"正如睡眠帶來夢境"
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.75,2:11:03.46,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,"As sleep brings dreams."
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.51,2:11:12.22,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,是哥倫布說的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.51,2:11:12.22,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Christopher Columbus.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.10,2:11:19.48,CHT,,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎光臨新世界
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.10,2:11:19.48,ENG,,0,0,0,!Effect,Welcome to the new world, sir.

